{"company_name": "nab-innovation-centre-vietnam", "job_name": "Senior NodeJS Engineer", "tag_list": "\nNodeJS\n\n\nJavaScript\n\n\nAWS\n", "location": "TNR Tower, 54A Nguyen Chi Thanh, Lang Thuong, Dong Da, Ha Noi", "three_reasons": "Very competitive remuneration package\nBuild products for millions of users in Australia\nHybrid and flexible working environment", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>We are seeking motivated Senior Backend Engineers, NodeJS who are passionate, results-focused to take accountability for the design and delivery of <strong>Microservices</strong> that will be used by banking applications. You will be part of our delivery team and will be responsible for providing technical leadership throughout all phases of the software delivery life cycle as we initiate a transformation of NAB technology. </p><p>We are one of Australia’s biggest banks – but we know that life’s about more than money. It’s about the connections we share with our customers, and the great things we can do to make life easier for them.</p><p>That’s why we’re so driven to do great things in the tech space. NAB is rapidly building a top-notch engineering capability and culture; adopting FinTech start-up mentality and financial innovation. We are working more agile than ever, so that we can deliver a great banking experience to our customers.</p><p><strong>YOUR JOB RESPONSIBILITIES </strong></p><ol>\n<li>Collaborate with other NAB's technology leaders towards improving and fulfilling the NAB technical direction;</li>\n<li>Evangelize and promote <strong>JavaScript</strong> - <strong>NodeJS</strong> best practices;</li>\n<li>Be passionate about JavaScript - NodeJS, stay relevant and understand how to implement advancement for existing or new systems;</li>\n<li>Design, develop, review, implement, and manage application code and services for the production and pre-release environments in NodeJS;</li>\n<li>Design, develop, review, implement, and manage continuous integration, build management and deployment scripts, systems, and any code as required;</li>\n<li>Participate in Agile software development, prototyping, and code review with international development teams to build scalable microservices-based products;</li>\n<li>Understand the requirements of the customer or business and utilize this knowledge to develop applications that are consistent with this;</li>\n<li>Work with delivery teams to achieve success through development using CI/CD and DevOps practices, processes and tooling;</li>\n<li>Provide robust coding practices and solid unit and component test coverage, and code debugging.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>Must have:</strong></p><ol>\n<li>\n<strong>At least 4 years</strong><span> </span> experience working in Software Development:<br>- Solid experience in <strong>JavaScript ES6</strong> (import/ export of Modules, promise, async wait, callbacks) and TypeScript working with <strong>NodeJS</strong>;<br>- Solid experience in using Jest<strong> </strong>Node.js unit testing or similar frameworks<br>- Experience working on microservices-based projects</li>\n<li>Solid experience in designing &amp; developing RESTful APIs<strong> </strong>and microservices-based systems;</li>\n<li>Solid DevOps and Continuous Delivery skillset: Experience in using <strong>Jenkins CI/CD</strong> pipelines and tools.</li>\n<li>Solid experience in <strong>Agile</strong> development environments;</li>\n<li>Well-versed in writing structured, well-documented, maintainable, and clean code;</li>\n<li>Excellent in <strong>problem-solving and analytical skills</strong>;</li>\n<li>Strong understanding of standard Software Engineering processes, Testing, and Agile methodology;</li>\n<li>Strong <strong>English </strong>communication skills (both verbal &amp; written), especially in the global software development environment;</li>\n<li>Experience in leading and coaching at least one software engineering team on various projects (Lead level).</li>\n</ol><p><strong>Nice to have:</strong></p><ol>\n<li>Experience in<strong> AWS </strong>and Containers (ECS, Kubernetes, Docker);</li>\n<li>Experience in the Banking or Financial Services industry;</li>\n<li>Experience in developing payments switching and processsing, terminal management systems.</li>\n<li>Experience in scripting (Bash, Python, Groovy, PowerShell, AWS CLI);</li>\n<li>Wide-ranging knowledge of various technologies (programming languages, frameworks, software architectures,..);</li>\n<li>Experience with developing microservices Java and SpringBoot;</li>\n<li>Experience in Front-End frameworks, specifically React.js;</li>\n<li>Any additional certification or training in IT, Business, Computer Science, or related area.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>THE BENEFITS AND PERKS</strong></p><ol>\n<li>Very competitive remuneration package</li>\n<li>Generous private family healthcare for yourself and two family members</li>\n<li>A solid team behind you - great people who love what they do</li>\n<li>The pleasant, enthusiastic, international work environment</li>\n<li>Opportunity for traveling &amp; training in Australia</li>\n<li>Brand new &amp; state of the art Agile offices</li>\n<li>Latest technologies, flexible working hours</li>\n<li>A promising training and career path</li>\n<li>Fun team activities &amp; outing</li>\n<li>English learning with native English teachers</li>\n</ol><p><strong>If this excites you, let's have a chat over a cup of coffee!</strong></p>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "dek-technologies", "job_name": "System Engineers (Linux)", "tag_list": "\nSystem Engineer\n\n\nLinux\n\n\nNetworking\n", "location": "9 - 11 Dong Da, Tan Binh, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "100% salary during probation, 13th salary\nPremium insurance (includes probation time)\nTechnical, Soft skill, English Training courses", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span>By joining the team, you have a chance to be involved in handling new request fulfillment, supply and support requests from different users in order to provide a best-in-class development and IT Infrastructure environment for users/use cases.</span></p><p><span>You will be a member of the global support team, work with many different customers and partners around the world in contributing to the satisfaction of the customers.</span></p><h4><span>Your responsibilities include but not limited to the following:</span></h4><ul>\n<li><span>Studies and analysis of environments based on priorities and serve as ground for further decisions and/or implementation</span></li>\n<li><span>Provide operating services including supplying and provisioning request from different users on the existing IT infrastructure environment</span></li>\n<li><span>Drive new IT service/solution/feature development</span></li>\n<li><span>Close cooperation with development team to drive the requirement towards the relevant teams</span></li>\n<li><span>Provide transformation of selected legacy environments &amp; solutions to modern cloud-based solutions</span></li>\n<li><span>​Actively contribute to our customer satisfaction</span></li>\n</ul><p><span><i>At DEK Technologies Vietnam, you will live with Agile &amp; Lean principles where employees are empowered at all levels to collaborate cross-functionally, to take pride in collective ownership, to improve yourself by continuously learning, practicing &amp; sharing with others.</i></span></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>Must have:</strong></p><ul>\n<li><span>University degree in Computer Science or Engineering</span></li>\n<li><span>At least 2-year relevant work experience</span></li>\n<li><span>Good English communication skill</span></li>\n<li><span>Ability to find the root cause of the problems in Linux</span></li>\n<li><span>Application troubleshooting</span></li>\n<li><span>Cross competency on Linux, Windows, Networking and Cloud</span></li>\n<li><span>Proactive monitoring of services and servers</span></li>\n<li><span>Act on failure Incidents and support requests from Customer</span></li>\n<li><span>Validation of requirements from customer and creation of new tickets</span></li>\n<li><span>Good knowledge about administering, configuring and upgrading of Linux OS: RHEL, SLES, UBUNTU, …</span></li>\n<li><span>Good Linux server troubleshooting: SUSE, RedHat, Ubuntu, CentOS, FTP, SSH, UDP, LDAP, Boot server, File system Management, AFS, NX/Citrix</span></li>\n</ul><p><span><strong>Nice to have:</strong></span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Security Knowledge: Policies. Roles, Rules, Users and Groups</span></li>\n<li><span>Cloud Services: Cloud services deployment (similar with AWS, Azure,... )</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>At DEK Technologies you will find yourself in an exciting career with:</p><ul>\n<li>Attractive compensation and benefits.</li>\n<li>Opportunities for short and long-term training/work overseas.</li>\n<li>An excellent working environment in developing tomorrow’s features.</li>\n<li>Open and honest culture where people are valued, treated fairly, trusted and empowered.</li>\n<li>Training and career development opportunities.</li>\n<li>40 flexible working hours per week from Monday to Friday.</li>\n<li>Attractive English classes and activities.</li>\n<li>Extra 24/7 Health and Accident Insurance.</li>\n<li>Annual health check-up.</li>\n<li>Annual company trip &amp; annual family day.</li>\n<li>Activities such as; sport &amp; music clubs, yoga &amp; piano classes.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "nab-innovation-centre-vietnam", "job_name": "Engineering Manager", "tag_list": "\nManager\n\n\nAgile\n\n\nScrum\n", "location": "E. Town Central, 11 Doan Van Bo, District 4, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Very competitive remuneration package\nBuild products for millions of users in Australia\nHybrid and flexible working environment", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>We are seeking a motivated <strong>Engineering Manager</strong> to help lead NAB’s Digital transformation efforts and reach your full potential by developing innovative products with cutting-edge cloud and microservices technologies.</p><p>The successful applicant will be accountable for the leadership of one or more engineering scrum teams to plan, deliver and support service features that deliver customer value and/or mature service capability.</p><p>The position is also accountable for executing the people leader fundamentals in line with NAB Policies, driving a learning-based culture with an ability to set and gain agreement for realistic and stretching objectives for the team.</p><p><strong>YOUR JOB RESPONSIBILITIES </strong></p><ol>\n<li>Manage multi Agile teams to deliver on engineering standards, sprint backlogs, and plans, engineers’ responsibilities and performance management, code quality, adherence to development, and testing guardrails.</li>\n<li>Manage milestones, deliverables, risks, and dependencies of the engineering teams.</li>\n<li>Educate the engineering teams and ensure the release of features to production comply with NAB risk management frameworks.</li>\n<li>Ability to create and maintain relationships with a wide range of stakeholders</li>\n<li>Be the voice of reason between speed and quality;</li>\n<li>Evangelist of the T-shaped working model; coach engineers to be T-shaped, versatile, and take responsibility outside their core disciplines;</li>\n<li>Line management (1:1 meetings, personal development &amp; training plan, career path, probation reviews, and performance reviews);</li>\n<li>Coach teams in applying Scrum and DevOps;</li>\n<li>Be responsible for continuous improvement of the teams;</li>\n<li>Lead initiatives for implementing efficient development and delivery processes;</li>\n<li>Drive a learning-based culture with an ability to set and gain agreement for realistic and stretching objectives for the team.</li>\n</ol><p><strong>Technical environment:</strong></p><ol>\n<li>Microservices architecture system</li>\n<li>Programming - Java, JavaScript, MV* patterns, Nodejs, ReactJS (including Redux), C#, NET Framework 4.7, etc. ASP.NET, MVC</li>\n<li>DevOps – Jenkins, Artifactory, SonarQube, GitHub, CloudFormation</li>\n<li>Cloud: Multi-Cloud, AWS (Lambda, Postgres, S3, API Gateway, CLI, SNS/SQS), Azure</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>Must have:</strong></p><ol>\n<li>10+ years working experience in Software Development; 5+ years experience in leading cross-functional Agile teams</li>\n<li>Solid understanding of Software Quality, DevOps environments</li>\n<li>Excellent experience in SDLC methodologies – Scrum, Kanban, Waterfall</li>\n<li>Proven ability to manage and deliver complex technology projects involve multiple engineering teams both onshore and offshore</li>\n<li>Real-world experience with large-scale Agile adoption, not just theoretical knowledge.</li>\n<li>Strong stakeholder management experience;</li>\n<li>Proven people leadership, team building, motivation, and coaching skills</li>\n<li>Experience in managing code and change management processes</li>\n<li>Experience with IT Service Management (e.g. Release Management) and experience with using Service Now or similar.</li>\n<li>Strong ability to communicate at both strategic and operational level internally and externally, making effective decisions balancing business and stakeholder needs</li>\n<li>Fluent English skills</li>\n</ol><p><strong>Nice to have:</strong></p><ol>\n<li>Agile – Certified Scrum Master (preferred)</li>\n<li>Experience in the Banking or Financial Services industry; (preferred)</li>\n<li>Fluent in English communication skills (both verbal &amp; written)</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>THE BENEFITS AND PERKS</strong></p><ol>\n<li>Very competitive remuneration package</li>\n<li>Generous private family healthcare for yourself and family members</li>\n<li>Build products for millions of users in Australia</li>\n<li>Hybrid and flexible working environment</li>\n<li>A solid team behind you - great people who love what they do</li>\n<li>The pleasant, enthusiastic, international work environment</li>\n<li>Opportunity for traveling &amp; training in Australia</li>\n<li>Brand new &amp; state of the art Agile offices</li>\n<li>Latest technologies, flexible working hours</li>\n<li>A promising training and career path</li>\n<li>Fun team activities &amp; outing</li>\n<li>English learning with native English teachers</li>\n</ol><p> </p>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "dek-technologies", "job_name": "Voice Over LTE/5G Software Engineer", "tag_list": "\nNetworking\n\n\nLinux\n\n\nC++\n\n\nFresher Accepted\n", "location": "9 - 11 Dong Da, Tan Binh, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "100% salary during probation, 13th salary\nPremium insurance (includes probation time)\nTechnical, Soft skill, English Training courses", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span><strong>Product Overview</strong></span></p><p><span>We are developing a Session Border Controller (SBC) in the IP Multimedia Subsystem (IMS), which is commonly used by many operators in telecommunication networks all over the world. The SBC is:</span></p><ul>\n<li><span>A carrier-class accessing and interconnecting IMS and other IP multimedia networks;</span></li>\n<li><span>A gateway to guarantee security, privacy, and quality of service for both signaling and media;</span></li>\n<li><span>One product for supporting multimedia IMS applications such as Voice over LTE (VoLTE), Video over LTE (ViLTE), WiFi-calling, SIP Trunking, Rich Communication Services (RCS), and interconnect scenarios;</span></li>\n<li><span>Deployed in Enterprise infrastructures or any carrier network delivering commercial residential, business, fixed-line, or mobile VoIP services;</span></li>\n</ul><p><span><strong>Responsibility</strong></span></p><p><span>By joining our distributed cross-functional teams between Sweden and Vietnam, you will be involved in the full system development lifecycle:</span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Analyze and propose the solution for new requirements requested by customers;</span></li>\n<li><span>Design and implement the feature solutions requested by customers;</span></li>\n<li><span>Design and execute the test scenarios from low-level to high-level testing;</span></li>\n<li><span>Track the testing results on the Continuous Integration (CI) system to ensure the quality of the feature development;</span></li>\n<li><span>Update documents to guide customers to use new features;</span></li>\n<li><span>Analyze and answer questions raised from customers towards the product and advise customers to use the released features properly;</span></li>\n<li><span>Support the customer in fixing product issues;</span></li>\n</ul><p><span><strong>Skills gained</strong></span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Enhance your ability to analyze, design, and implement new features;</span></li>\n<li><span>Enhance problem-solving skills related to real-life situations for professional clients;</span></li>\n<li><span>Working within a professional development process framework defined by an international telecommunication company;</span></li>\n<li><span>Upgrade networking and system knowledge such as security, load balancing, system stabilization, system integration, etc;</span></li>\n<li><span>Improve your understanding of the voice network system;</span></li>\n<li><span>Work with a huge telecommunication product that is widely used around the world;</span></li>\n</ul><p><span><i>You will live a true Agile; Lean culture where employees are empowered at all levels to collaborate and take ownership. At DEK Vietnam, we constantly run the Scrum mentorship and Agile Coaching programs to help build up your career path.</i></span></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span><strong>If you have just graduated from University with a Bachelor's Degree in either Information Technology, Computer Science or a related degree with:</strong></span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Voice Over IP (VoIP) technology (Opensips, IP-PBX, Asterisk, Kamailio, Oracle Communication Application Server, etc.);</span></li>\n<li><span>Mobile Telecommunication technology (GSM, WCDMA, LTE, 5G, IMS, etc.);</span></li>\n<li><span>Basic programming or scripting experience;</span></li>\n<li><span>High teamwork spirit;</span></li>\n<li><span>Eager to learn new technologies;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>At DEK Technologies you will find yourself in an exciting career with:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Attractive compensation and benefits.</li>\n<li>Opportunities for short and long-term training/work overseas.</li>\n<li>An excellent working environment in developing tomorrow’s features.</li>\n<li>Open and honest culture where people are valued, treated fairly, trusted and empowered.</li>\n<li>Training and career development opportunities.</li>\n<li>40 flexible working hours per week from Monday to Friday.</li>\n<li>Attractive English classes and activities.</li>\n<li>Extra 24/7 Health and Accident Insurance.</li>\n<li>Annual health check-up.</li>\n<li>Annual company trip &amp; annual family day.</li>\n<li>Activities such as; sport &amp; music clubs, yoga &amp; piano classes.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "dek-technologies", "job_name": "Embedded Software Developers (C++, Linux)", "tag_list": "\nEmbedded\n\n\nLinux\n\n\nC++\n", "location": "9 - 11 Dong Da, Tan Binh, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "100% salary during probation, 13th salary\nPremium insurance (includes probation time)\nTechnical, Soft skill, English Training courses", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>As a key member of the Software Engineering team, you will be involved in the delivery of projects for both internal and external projects – from initial concept design, advising leading global automotive manufacturers on all aspects of the Software Development Life Cycle, right through to design for testing and manufacture on internal projects. Working with C++, you will apply your skills and knowledge of the Linux Operating Systems, processor architecture and hardware designs to develop computer vision systems such as driver monitoring that comply to relevant safety and process standards.</p><p>Our close-knit team fosters an environment of product innovation, quality software, rapid product iteration and collaboration on a wide range of hardware and software products, where you will be responsible for:</p><ul>\n<li>Designing, implementing and testing Linux kernel drivers/applications for the Driver Monitoring solution for a number of driver monitoring applications</li>\n<li>Designing, developing and problem-solving embedded systems – including prototyping of concepts as well as optimizing and improving system architecture</li>\n</ul><p><i>At DEK Technologies Vietnam, you will live with Agile &amp; Lean principles where employees are empowered at all levels to collaborate cross-functionally, to take pride in collective ownership, to improve yourself by continuously learning, practicing &amp; sharing with others.</i></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>University with a Bachelor's Degree in either Information Technology, Computer Science or a related degree with:</p><ul>\n<li>Experience developing production-quality C++ code</li>\n<li>Experience writing code for multi-core SoCs and multi-threading system</li>\n<li>Experience developing embedded Linux kernel drivers/applications</li>\n</ul><p>Nice to have:</p><ul>\n<li>Good understanding on CPU-base architecture, Embedded System, and boot loaders.</li>\n<li>Have some basic working knowledge of UART, SPI, I2C, EPROM, SRAM, and Flash Memory.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>At DEK Technologies you will find yourself in an exciting career with:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Attractive compensation and benefits</li>\n<li>Opportunities for short and long-term training/work overseas</li>\n<li>An excellent working environment in developing tomorrow’s features</li>\n<li>Open and honest culture where people are valued, treated fairly, trusted and empowered</li>\n<li>Training and career development opportunities</li>\n<li>40 flexible working hours per week from Monday to Friday</li>\n<li>Attractive English classes and activities</li>\n<li>Extra 24/7 Health and Accident Insurance</li>\n<li>Annual health check-up</li>\n<li>Annual company trip &amp; annual family day</li>\n<li>Activities such as; sport &amp; music clubs, yoga &amp; piano classes</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "dek-technologies", "job_name": "Embedded Software Testers", "tag_list": "\nTester\n\n\nPython\n\n\nEmbedded\n", "location": "9 - 11 Dong Da, Tan Binh, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "100% salary during probation, 13th salary\nPremium insurance (includes probation time)\nTechnical, Soft skill, English Training courses", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span>As a key member of our Software Test Engineering team, you will be responsible for the verification and validation of the Driver Monitoring System. You will be responsible for the verification and validation of the DMS at different levels. You will design and develop test cases for execution on multiple platforms. You will collaborate with a world class team of Engineers as we work together to deliver best in class technology.</span><br><br><span>Your responsibilities include but are not limited to the following:</span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Design specifications for Driver Monitoring System</span></li>\n<li><span>Develop and execute the automation test script</span></li>\n<li><span>Design and develop an automation test framework</span></li>\n<li><span>Interface with key stakeholders on project test activities</span></li>\n</ul><p><i>At DEK Technologies Vietnam, you will live with Agile &amp; Lean principles where employees are empowered at all levels to collaborate cross-functionally, to take pride in collective ownership, to improve yourself by continuously learning, practicing &amp; sharing with others.</i></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span><strong>A University Qualification in Software Engineering or a related degree with experiences.</strong></span></p><p>*** Knowledge and Skill Requirements:</p><ul>\n<li><span>At least 2 years of experience as Software Tester, Embedded Software Testing or similar position;</span></li>\n<li><span>Knowledge of testing methodologies, testing process, quality models, standards;</span></li>\n<li><span>Experience with automation test in any testing level using programming languages such as C, C++Python, Bash Script, etc</span></li>\n</ul><p><span>*** Soft skills:</span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Good English in verbal and written.</span></li>\n<li><span>Good at teamwork and willing to work independently.</span></li>\n<li><span>Analytical and problem-solving capabilities.</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>At DEK Technologies you will find yourself in an exciting career with:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Attractive compensation and benefits</li>\n<li>Opportunities for short and long-term training/work overseas</li>\n<li>An excellent working environment in developing tomorrow’s features</li>\n<li>Open and honest culture where people are valued, treated fairly, trusted and empowered</li>\n<li>Training and career development opportunities</li>\n<li>40 flexible working hours per week from Monday to Friday</li>\n<li><span>Interesting English classes and activities</span></li>\n<li>Extra 24/7 Health and Accident Insurance</li>\n<li>Annual health check-up</li>\n<li>Annual company trip &amp; annual family day</li>\n<li>Activities such as; sport &amp; music clubs, yoga &amp; piano classes</li>\n<li>Working in HCM's office or Remotely work from other provinces</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "dek-technologies", "job_name": "ReactJS Developer (JavaScript, HTML5)", "tag_list": "\nReactJS\n\n\nHTML5\n\n\nJavaScript\n", "location": "9 - 11 Dong Da, Tan Binh, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "100% salary during probation, 13th salary\nPremium insurance (includes probation time)\nTechnical, Soft skill, English Training courses", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span>Are you: </span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Accountable, result driven, self-driven, pro-active and have the ability to work independently?</span></li>\n<li><span>A fast learner, with high developed analytical thinking?</span></li>\n<li><span>A good problem solving, logical thinking, high-quality coding engineer?</span></li>\n<li><span>Interested in learning new things?</span></li>\n</ul><p><span>We are looking for proficient ReactJS developers. You’ll be part of a cross-functional team that’s responsible on front-end web development to create reusable ReactJS components for highly-responsive user interface. </span></p><p><span><i>At DEK Technologies Vietnam, you will live with Agile &amp; Lean principles where employees are empowered at all levels to collaborate cross-functionally, to take pride in collective ownership, to improve yourself by continuously learning, practicing &amp; sharing with others.</i></span></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span><strong>Required skills:</strong></span></p><ul>\n<li><span>2+ years’ experience as a Front-end Developer or similar role</span></li>\n<li><span>Knowledge of multiple front-end languages and libraries (e.g., HTML/ CSS, JavaScript, XML, jQuery)</span></li>\n<li><span>Familiarity with databases (e.g., MySQL, MongoDB), web servers (e.g., Apache) </span></li>\n<li><span>Proficiency of React.js and its core principles</span></li>\n<li><span>Experience with popular React.js workflows (such as Flux or Redux)</span></li>\n<li><span>Good experienced with Web API, Web Services, REST API, JSON, XML</span></li>\n<li><span>Experience with common front-end development tools such as Babel, Webpack, NPM…</span></li>\n</ul><p><span><strong>Nice to have:</strong></span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Experience with Docker</span></li>\n<li><span>Experience with building and deploying system by using automation tools such as Jenkins, SonarQube</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>At DEK Technologies you will find yourself in an exciting career with:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Attractive, competitive salary and incentives</li>\n<li>Opportunities for short and long-term training/work overseas</li>\n<li>An excellent working environment in developing tomorrow’s features</li>\n<li>Open and honest culture where people are valued, treated fairly, trusted and empowered</li>\n<li>Training and career development opportunities</li>\n<li>40 flexible working hours per week from Monday to Friday</li>\n<li>English classes 3 hours a week with qualified foreign teachers</li>\n<li>Extra 24/7 Health and Accident Insurance</li>\n<li>Annual health check-up</li>\n<li>Annual company trip &amp; annual family day</li>\n<li>Activities such as; sport &amp; music clubs, yoga &amp; piano classes</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "dek-technologies", "job_name": "CI Engineer", "tag_list": "\nDevOps\n\n\nPython\n\n\nLinux\n", "location": "9 - 11 Dong Da, Tan Binh, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "100% salary during probation, 13th salary\nPremium insurance (includes probation time)\nTechnical, Soft skill, English Training courses", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span>As a Continuous Integration (CI) Engineer, you will own the build/release pipeline operation of the development system. Your job will be involved in:</span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Troubleshoot issues, suggest, implement solutions and write high-quality code in Groovy for CI pipelines and infrastructure</span></li>\n<li><span>Understand the CI automation workflow (e.g., building, testing, deploying and performance test)</span></li>\n<li><span>Work with Software Engineer to develop and support the CI process</span></li>\n<li><span>Continuously improve together with the team</span></li>\n</ul><p><span><i>At DEK Technologies Vietnam, you will live with Agile &amp; Lean principles where employees are empowered at all levels to collaborate cross-functionally, to take pride in collective ownership, to improve yourself by continuously learning, practicing &amp; sharing with others.</i></span></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span><strong>Must have:</strong></span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Experienced with CI pipeline of Jenkins</span></li>\n<li><span>Experienced with Linux/Unix working environment</span></li>\n<li><span>Experienced using Docker and Ansible</span></li>\n<li><span>Experienced of managing Openstack, KVM</span></li>\n<li><span>Experienced either Bash Script, Python or Java language</span></li>\n</ul><p><span><strong>Nice to have:</strong></span></p><ul><li><span>Familiar with Git version control tool</span></li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>At DEK Technologies you will find yourself in an exciting career with:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Attractive, competitive salary and incentives</li>\n<li>Opportunities for short and long-term training/work overseas</li>\n<li>An excellent working environment in developing tomorrow’s features</li>\n<li>Open and honest culture where people are valued, treated fairly, trusted and empowered</li>\n<li>Training and career development opportunities</li>\n<li>40 flexible working hours per week from Monday to Friday</li>\n<li>English classes 3 hours a week with qualified foreign teachers</li>\n<li>Extra 24/7 Health and Accident Insurance</li>\n<li>Annual health check-up</li>\n<li>Annual company trip &amp; annual family day</li>\n<li>Activities such as; sport &amp; music clubs, yoga &amp; piano classes</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "dek-technologies", "job_name": "Embedded System Testers", "tag_list": "\nTester\n\n\nC++\n\n\nEmbedded\n", "location": "9 - 11 Dong Da, Tan Binh, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "100% salary during probation, 13th salary\nPremium insurance (includes probation time)\nTechnical, Soft skill, English Training courses", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span>As a key member of our Software Test Engineering team, you will work with the modern Driver Monitoring System (DMS). It is also known as driver attention monitor, a vehicle safety system to assess the driver's alertness and warn the driver if needed. The DMS consists of a small infrared camera and near infrared lighting pods mounted on the driver’s side vehicle cockpit and is focused toward the driver’s face. The raw video from the camera is passed to main processing where it is processed real-time and measures attention by continuously searching for and tracking the features of the driver’s face and eyes. Simultaneously tracking the multiple points on the face, eyelids and pupils in a large head box over large and sudden head rotations and eye gaze angles, operating robustly in all foreseeable driving conditions including direct sunshine and total darkness, regardless of race or ethnicity, and even when the driver is wearing sunglasses is key to securing a highly reliable real-time core signal set for our classifiers for driver attention and driver state to work from.</span></p><p><span>You will be responsible for the verification and validation of the DMS at different levels. You will design and develop tests cases for execution on multiple platforms. You will collaborate with a world class team of Engineers as we work together to deliver best in class technology.</span></p><p><span>Your responsibilities include but not limited to the following:</span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Design specifications for Driver Monitoring System</span></li>\n<li><span>Develop and execute automation test script</span></li>\n<li><span>Design and develop automation test framework</span></li>\n<li><span>Interface with key stakeholders on project test activities</span></li>\n</ul><p><span>At DEK Technologies Vietnam, you will live with Agile &amp; Lean principles where employees are empowered at all levels to collaborate cross-functionally, to take pride in collective ownership, to improve yourself by continuously learning, practicing &amp; sharing with others.</span></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span><strong>A University Qualification in Software Engineering or a related degree with experience:</strong></span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Experience with embedded system testing</span></li>\n<li><span>Knowledge of testing methodologies, testing process, quality models, standards</span></li>\n<li><span>Experience with automation test in any testing level using programming languages such as C, C++, Python, or NI TestStand</span></li>\n<li><span>Good at English communication</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>At DEK Technologies you will find yourself in an exciting career with:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Attractive compensation and benefits</li>\n<li>Opportunities for short and long-term training/work overseas</li>\n<li>An excellent working environment in developing tomorrow’s features</li>\n<li>Open and honest culture where people are valued, treated fairly, trusted and empowered</li>\n<li>Training and career development opportunities</li>\n<li>40 flexible working hours per week from Monday to Friday</li>\n<li>Attractive English classes and activities</li>\n<li>Extra 24/7 Health and Accident Insurance</li>\n<li>Annual health check-up</li>\n<li>Annual company trip &amp; annual family day</li>\n<li>Activities such as; sport &amp; music clubs, yoga &amp; piano classes</li>\n<li>Working in HCM's office or Remotely work from other provinces</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
