utomation tools (e.g., Jenkins, SonarQube)</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>At DEK Technologies you will find yourself in an exciting career with:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Attractive, competitive salary and incentives</li>\n<li>Opportunities for short and long-term training/work overseas</li>\n<li>An excellent working environment in developing tomorrow’s features</li>\n<li>Open and honest culture where people are valued, treated fairly, trusted and empowered</li>\n<li>Training and career development opportunities</li>\n<li>40 flexible working hours per week from Monday to Friday</li>\n<li>English classes 3 hours a week with qualified foreign teachers</li>\n<li>Extra 24/7 Health and Accident Insurance</li>\n<li>Annual health check-up</li>\n<li>Annual company trip &amp; annual family day</li>\n<li>Activities such as; sport &amp; music clubs, yoga &amp; piano classes</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "techcombank", "job_name": "Senior Java Developer", "tag_list": "\nJava\n\n\nAgile\n\n\nSpring\n", "location": "C5 Building Tower, D’Capitale Tower, 119 Tran Duy Hung, Cau Giay, Ha Noi", "three_reasons": "Top-tier banking environment in Vietnam\nChallenging opportunities for the “Greater” You\nAttractive career path and benefits", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span><strong>I. Job Purpose:</strong></span></p><p><span>• The job holder will assist in the design and development of server-side web applications by developing and maintaining functional and stable web applications to meet customer needs.</span></p><p><span>• The job holder will also be involved in troubleshooting and debugging backend systems to support functionality of applications.</span></p><p><span><strong>II. Key Accountabilities:</strong></span></p><p><span><i><strong>A. Software Development</strong></i></span></p><p><span>• Responsible for ensuring that the bank's digital platforms work well by managing back end site databases, performance issues, security and that the server, application and database communicate with each other.</span></p><p><span>• Responsible for collaborating with business tribes to understand the needs and technical requirements before building a web application.</span></p><p><span>• Responsible for the server-side web application logic and integration with front-end codes</span></p><p><span>• Collaborate with Front End Developers to design more functional and cohesive codes to enhance user experience.</span></p><p><span>• Responsible for driving the application lifecycle with a key focus in coding and debugging of web applications based on feedback from testers and users.</span></p><p><span>• Compile and analyze data, process and codes to troubleshoot problems and identify areas for improvement.</span></p><p><span><i><strong>B. Software Documentation</strong></i></span></p><p><span>• Work closely with tribe and squad members to translate business requirements into technical design documents.</span></p><p><span>• Review and implement technical requirement documents by coding flowcharts, layouts, diagrams, charts, code comments and guides for the program.</span></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span><i><strong>A. Domain Expertise</strong></i></span></p><p><span>• 4 to 10 years of relevant experience in software development</span></p><p><span>• Basic knowledge in Java backend web development using scripting languages / frameworks </span></p><p><span>• Experience working with relational DBMS and SQL</span></p><p><span>• Experience working in a source-controlled environment, such as Git or TFVC</span></p><p><span>• Basic understanding of API design and implementation</span></p><p><span>• Basic understanding of Spring &amp; Spring related projects</span></p><p><span><i><strong>B. Agile / Digital Experience</strong></i></span></p><p><span>• Understands Agile principles, practices and Scrum methodologies.</span></p><p><span>• Experience working in Agile teams to support digital transformation projects.</span></p><p><span><i><strong>C. Qualifications</strong></i></span></p><p><span>• Bachelor's degree in computer science, software engineering or information technology</span></p><p><span><i><strong>D. Personal Attributes</strong></i></span></p><p><span>• Passionate about technology and excited about the impact of emerging / disruptive technologies</span></p><p><span>• Ownership mindset with a focus on getting things fixed, not simply discovered</span></p><p><span>• A self-starter who thrives in an environment that fosters entrepreneurial thinking and innovation</span></p><p><span>• Believes in the non-hierarchical culture of collaboration, transparency and trust across the team</span></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>WHY BECOME IT/DATA EXPERTS AT TECHCOMBANK?</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Investing <strong>over 300 million USD</strong> to develop large-scale IT projects, Techcombank is one of the leading bank in Technology trends in Vietnam</li>\n<li>You will grow with Techcombank by having the opportunity to learn from <strong>top experts</strong> from across the world</li>\n<li>Techcombank provides a <strong>rewarding remuneration structure</strong> that commensurate with your achievement and contribution</li>\n<li>Techcombank is the <strong>Top 2 Best place to work </strong>in the banking industry where you can experience various exciting activities throughout the year: Company anniversary, Team building, Active Saturday Off, Year End Party, etc.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "dek-technologies", "job_name": "10 Software Developers (Fresher)", "tag_list": "\nC++\n\n\nC language\n\n\nPython\n\n\nFresher Accepted\n", "location": "9 - 11 Dong Da, Tan Binh, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "100% salary during probation, 13th salary\nPremium insurance (includes probation time)\nTechnical, Soft skill, English Training courses", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span>We have many wonderful new opportunities for IT Freshers in our existing teams as well as new teams. You can be involved in software development, maintenance, and/or testing for one of the following products:</span></p><ul>\n<li><span>New generation of mobile core network infrastructure that enables various types of multimedia services to end-users using common TCP/IP-based protocols</span></li>\n<li><span>A high capacity, high availability, scalability cluster platform used mission-critical products that can serve extremely huge number of users at the same time.</span></li>\n<li><span>Linux Operating System (OS) customization;</span></li>\n<li><span>You will take opportunities to work with new technologies such as Voice over LTE (VoLTE), OpenStack, Virtualization (KVM, VMware), …</span></li>\n</ul><p><span><i>You will live a true Agile; Lean culture where employees are empowered at all levels to collaborate and take ownership. At DEK Vietnam, we constantly run the Scrum mentorship and Agile Coaching programs to help build up your career path.</i></span></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span><strong>If you have just graduated from University with a Bachelor Degree in either Information Technology, Computer Science or a related degree with:</strong></span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Strong IT background.</span></li>\n<li><span>Knowledge of at least one programming language (ex: C/C++, Python, Java, ...)</span></li>\n<li><span>Willing to learn other programming languages.</span></li>\n<li><span>High teamwork spirit.</span></li>\n<li><span>Basic English communication.</span></li>\n</ul><p>Passionate to develop a career in a professional and multicultural environment?</p><p><span>Email your English CV, Score transcript, AND thesis subject to us now!</span></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>At DEK Technologies you will find yourself in an exciting career with:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Attractive compensation and benefits.</li>\n<li>Opportunities for short and long-term training/work overseas.</li>\n<li>An excellent working environment in developing tomorrow’s features.</li>\n<li>Open and honest culture where people are valued, treated fairly, trusted and empowered.</li>\n<li>Training and career development opportunities.</li>\n<li>40 flexible working hours per week from Monday to Friday.</li>\n<li>Attractive English classes and activities.</li>\n<li>Extra 24/7 Health and Accident Insurance.</li>\n<li>Annual health check-up.</li>\n<li>Annual company trip &amp; annual family day.</li>\n<li>Activities such as; sport &amp; music clubs, yoga &amp; piano classes.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "techcombank", "job_name": "Data Analyst ", "tag_list": "\nData Analyst\n\n\nPython\n\n\nSQL\n", "location": "Số 23 Lê Duẩn, phường Bến Nghé, District 1, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Top-tier banking environment in Vietnam\nChallenging opportunities for the “Greater” You\nAttractive career path and benefits", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span>The Data Analyst candidate will manage all reconciliation reports to support jobs between Operation team and Data teams. The job concentrates to build/maintain automate code loop from getting data from exchange data server, by working with Data Engineers, collecting data from internal/external databases, and supporting OPS to validate on the data to make sure all data is consistent therefor minimize the risk. The position also supports on other tasks related if needed </span></p><p><span><strong>Responsibilities</strong> </span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Working with programmers, engineers, and management heads to building BI solutions using existed cloud provided services, particularly, the automate reconciliation processes for reconciliation reports. </span></li>\n<li><span>Working with business sides/ OPS side in dentifying, creating, preparing data required for modern BI solutions also proposing business system modifications and devising data governance strategies </span></li>\n<li><span>Creating and documenting the tests to meet requirements. </span></li>\n<li><span>Maintaining, tuning and adapting applications to keep them performing to specifications. </span></li>\n<li><span>Proactive to provide and suggest meaningful solution to optimize the process </span></li>\n<li><span>Proactive communicate, align and work with internal and external stakeholder to get the task done </span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li><span>Excellent knowledge of SQL/ Oracle analytical tools, and Python, other languages are preferable (PySpark, Java, C). </span></li>\n<li><span>Sufficient knowledge of Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Outlook,…). </span></li>\n<li><span>Proficient in data visualization tools (Tableau, PowerBI,) is a plus. </span></li>\n<li><span>Good to know or experience in Big Data technologies (Hadoop, Spark, Data Bricks, Snowflake). </span></li>\n<li><span>Excellent English reporting skills. </span></li>\n<li><span>A methodical and logical approach, ability to plan work and meet deadlines. </span></li>\n<li><span>An understanding of the ethics of gathering and working with data, accuracy, and attention to detail. </span></li>\n<li><span>Open mindset, ability to quickly adapt new technologies /new bank working environment and learn new practice. </span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>WHY BECOME IT/DATA EXPERTS AT TECHCOMBANK?</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Investing <strong>over 300 million USD</strong> to develop large-scale IT projects, Techcombank is one of the leading bank in Technology trends in Vietnam</li>\n<li>You will grow with Techcombank by having the opportunity to learn from <strong>top experts</strong> from across the world</li>\n<li>Techcombank provides a <strong>rewarding remuneration structure</strong> that commensurate with your achievement and contribution</li>\n<li>Techcombank is the <strong>Top 2 Best place to work </strong>in the banking industry where you can experience various exciting activities throughout the year: Company anniversary, Team building, Active Saturday Off, Year End Party, etc.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
