>\n<li>Design pattern, data structure and algorithms.</li>\n<li>Good English communication skills</li>\n<li>Experience in and success with Agile software development methodologies, especially Scrum.</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Nice to have:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Experience in, and preference for, developing software using continuous integration and continuous delivery practices.</li>\n<li>Experience with consuming and building microservices and REST APIs</li>\n<li>Experience building apps on AWS and familiarity with technologies like IAM, API gateway, elastic load balancing, S3, Cognito, cloud front, cloud watch, SQS, SNS, step functions, etc.</li>\n<li>Proficient understanding of code versioning tools, such as Git</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>High paying Salary, Full Salary in Probation.</li>\n<li>13th-month Salary and Performance Bonus</li>\n<li>Flexible 14 days Leave</li>\n<li>Private Health Insurance</li>\n<li>Flexible Timings,  5 days working</li>\n<li>Monthly Party and Yearly Outings</li>\n<li>Working with high skilled Developers on a Global Product with Millions of Users</li>\n<li>Fully stocked Pantry</li>\n<li>Annual Health Checkup</li>\n<li>Laptop of your choice</li>\n<li>Friendly International Working Environment</li>\n<li>Order Books, Buy online learning Material</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
