least 3 years of experience working as a Data Scientist or AI engineer position</li>\n<li>Having a strong background in statistics (At least confident in mathematics)</li>\n<li>Proficient with frameworks: Pytorch, TensorFlow</li>\n<li>Having good knowledge and experience about MLOps</li>\n<li>Having a good knowledge of visualization, capable of using BI tools is a plus</li>\n<li>Proficient in Python, C/C++ programming languages</li>\n<li>Good logical &amp; critical thinking skills, hard-working and responsible at work.</li>\n<li>Effective communication skills.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Competitive salary: upto $2500</li>\n<li>14 months' salary a year</li>\n<li>Opportunity to receive Stock Option.</li>\n<li>To fully participate in the regimes prescribed by the State such as social insurance, health insurance, unemployment insurance, and annual leave.</li>\n<li>Be trained and work directly with experienced experts in the field of AI.</li>\n<li>Have the opportunity to do challenging things, develop your full potential</li>\n<li>Participate in team building sessions, have fun monthly with the Company;</li>\n<li>Enjoy full benefits (Happiness, birthday...);</li>\n<li>Young, comfortable working environment, dynamic startup spirit.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "onpoint", "job_name": "QC Lead (QA QC, Tester)", "tag_list": "\nQA QC\n\n\nTeam Leader\n\n\nTester\n", "location": " Floor 4, AB Building, 27B Nguyen Dinh Chieu,, District 1, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Opportunity for regional scale (South East Asia)\nEnrich your skills and develop your potential\nEnjoy motivating working conditions", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span>OnPoint is the largest E-commerce enabler in Vietnam, providing end-to-end services, helping brands to accelerate and become more successful online in Vietnam and SEA region. OnPoint's mission is to make E-commerce easy for brands, to create sustainable values for businesses, consumers, and partners.</span></p><p><span>It's a privilege for us to serve top-tier clients. Our integrated capabilities encompass all aspects of the E-commerce value chain covering store commercial and operations, digital marketing, customer services, warehousing, and fulfillment. We help a brand execute their E-com strategies by selling their goods directly to customers online or by providing services to assist with their E-com operations. Our business ranges from the largest online shopping platforms as well as social shopping channels.</span></p><p><span>Since day one, we have dedicated ourselves to the needs of our brand partners. We work closely to ensure our direction and thought processes are tightly aligned with their needs</span></p><p><span>Join us, make a difference, and create value for life!</span></p><p><span><strong>Reporting to the </strong></span><span><strong>Chief Technology Officer </strong></span><span><strong>you will be responsible for:</strong></span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Assist in review and development of project specifications for code compliance and constructability within industry standards</span></li>\n<li><span>Assist and provide leadership in the development of robust QC processes and standards to enable the client’s successful project completion</span></li>\n<li><span>Provide training of personnel to ensure awareness of quality procedures and specific responsibilities in the QC process, including the interface and response to audits such as those conducted by the client or third parties (stakeholders supporting the project)</span></li>\n<li><span>Develop, manage, and implement related quality control plans as Test Plan, Test Strategy, Test Procedure, Test Suite, Test cases, Test Script, Test scenario, and Test condition as required by projects.</span></li>\n<li><span>Manage the QC control process and ensure the process, best practices, and quality standards are adhered to by the team, related project teams, and stakeholders.</span></li>\n<li><span>Communicate with stakeholders to update statuses of your plan and related quality issues, ensure their engagements in requirements and project deliverable.</span></li>\n<li><span>Improve quality control process, tools, techniques, and testing methodology.</span></li>\n<li><span>Maximize or optimize possibilities of automation testing and manual testing during the development life cycle as required by the project.</span></li>\n<li><span>Participate in R&amp;D activities of the team.</span></li>\n<li><span>Support your manager and directors in making Test Policy, Test Processes.</span></li>\n<li><span>Perform performance monitoring and annual review for the team.</span></li>\n<li><span>Build up communication and collaboration among QC team members.</span></li>\n<li><span>Ensure good cooperation between QC teams and other functional teams.</span></li>\n<li><span>Report to your direct manager and related project managers as required.</span></li>\n<li><span>Regularly analyze and make statistical quality data reports and propose approaches to improve.</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li><span>Bachelor’s degree in computer science, information systems, or a related field.</span></li>\n<li><span>Having 4+ years in Software testing and 1 year at the same level</span></li>\n<li><span>Experience in creating Test Plans, Test Cases, and Test Reports.</span></li>\n<li><span>Minimum of 3 years' experience management role and manage the team size including more than 5 members.</span></li>\n<li><span>Good understanding of software testing, related concepts, practices, life cycle, process, approaches, and methodologies.</span></li>\n<li><span>Good English writing skills.</span></li>\n<li><span>Great interest in Ecommerce</span></li>\n<li><span>Experience with agile development processes and frequent release cycles.</span></li>\n<li><span>Great interest in e-Commerce.</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>Hone your creativity, invent and innovate, and set your own highest standards within a nurturing, equal opportunity environment. With our tremendous growth, we seek dynamic, entrepreneurial and broad-minded individuals to join us.</p><p> </p>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "shinhan-ds", "job_name": "System Engineer", "tag_list": "\nSystem Engineer\n\n\nSystem Admin\n\n\nIT Support\n\n\nFresher Accepted\n", "location": "Centec Tower, District 3, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Work environment that focus solely on development\nTraining opportunities with experts\n13th-14th month salary & Incentive Programs", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>System Construction &amp; Technical support, Internal System management. (H/W, Server/Storage Mgt, OS, Middle Ware, VMWare)</li>\n<li>Maintaining system functionality by testing computer components</li>\n<li>Maintain a working log detailing all required system updates, as well as the date of completion </li>\n<li>Resolve technical issues related to network interruptions</li>\n<li>Actively update, maintain and monitor all aspects of computer networks</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Graduate college or university with a major in Information Technology, Computer Science, or Software Engineering or related fields.</li>\n<li>From 5 years of experience in the relevant job or related technical field.</li>\n<li>Experience with one or more than one of these (System Design/Construction/Management/Technical support). </li>\n<li>Experience with Unix (HP-UX) or X86 Server (HPE, Dell EMC) management.</li>\n<li>Experience with Cloud or Virtualization Management.</li>\n<li>Good problem-solving &amp; communication skills. </li>\n<li>Detail-oriented, proactive, and fast learner.</li>\n<li>English fluently</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Preferred</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Able to design, build, and tune infrastructure architecture. </li>\n<li>Experience with using Open-source software.</li>\n<li>Great to have one of these certificates: RedHat RHCE, RHCA / Vmware VCP, VCTA ... / AWS Solution Architect Associate ...</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>Our company provides an opportunity to grow as an expert-Banking IT in Vietnam<br>You can learn about Banking concepts and know-how from Korea specialized developers<br>In addition, We have plans to expand our company to Indonesia, Myanmar, Philippines<br>We plan to offer training for outstanding employees in Korea. </p><ul>\n<li>Salary: you will be happy.</li>\n<li>Performance review: twice a year.</li>\n<li>Incentive Programs to congratulate members' development.</li>\n<li>Company Trips, monthly/weekly activities, and events.</li>\n<li>Health check once a year and advanced healthcare program.</li>\n<li>Free snacks, coffee, sponsored pizza or chicken &amp; beer parties.</li>\n<li>Work onsite with foreign teams for the short or long term.</li>\n<li>Your solutions and opinions are heard.<br> </li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
