to grow as an expert-Banking IT in Vietnam<br>You can learn about Banking concepts and know-how from Korea specialized developers<br>In addition, We have plans to expand our company to Indonesia, Myanmar, Philippines<br>We plan to offer training for outstanding employees in Korea. <br><br>- Salary: you will be happy.<br>- Performance review: twice a year.<br>- Incentive Programs to congratulate members' development.<br>- Company Trips, monthly/weekly activities, and events.<br>- Health check once a year and advanced healthcare program.<br>- Free snacks, coffee, sponsored pizza or chicken &amp; beer parties.<br>- Work onsite with foreign teams for the short or long term.<br>- Your solutions and opinions are heard.<br> </p>\n</div>"}
