{"company_name": "de-heus-asia", "job_name": "Application Engineer", "tag_list": "\nMySQL\n\n\nSoftware Architect\n\n\nIT Support\n", "location": "Tòa nhà Sofic, 10 Đường Mai Chí Thọ, Quận 2, Thu Duc City, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Professional & global working environment\nLots of training & development opportunities\n Health-care insurances by international provider", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span><strong>JOB PURPOSE :</strong></span><br><span>Work in technical supporting roles, main purposes of this role are:</span><br><span>- Involve in Project team as technical part for integration</span><br><span>- Provide 1st level technical support toward requests, issues or problems that are reported by users.</span><br><span>- Analyse and be able to develop, customize &amp; maintain printouts &amp; analysis reports.</span><br><span>- Participate to system development projects according to assigned role.</span><br><span>- Ready to travel</span><br><br><span><strong>KEY ACTIVITIES:</strong></span><br><span><strong>1. Rolling out application:</strong></span><br><span>- Involve in all stage of project: prepare test environment, support to test and support to rolling out.</span><br><span>- Onside implementing system (D365, DH App, and others as requested)</span><br><span>- Support to install and configure system</span><br><span>- Document all technical needed to able to roll out in next factories quickly and safety.</span><br><span><strong>2. Technical support</strong></span><br><span>- Working with supplier to build integration base on direction of project team and assure it work as expected.</span><br><span>- Work together with functional to solve technical issues and data related to integration between inside DH App or with ERP.</span><br><span>- Configure integration if new request</span><br><span>- Support to install and configure applications (Databases, execute files, configuration related to systems)</span><br><span>- Prepare and execute plan of backup solution of De Heus Application</span><br><span>- Support to prepare Recovery procedure including database, execute files, docker, windows and configuration need.</span><br><span><strong>3. Develop and maintain reports/printouts</strong></span><br><span>- Support to analyse and develop/modify all printouts in De Heus Application</span><br><span>- Support to roll out reports or printouts to factories and end-users</span><br><span>- Querying and database programming (triggers, procedures, functions)</span><br><span>- Creating reports with Reporting Services, Crystal Report)</span><br><span><strong>4. Enhance system:</strong></span><br><span>- Support to enhance performance of system (enhance query performance in query, and configuration of SQL Server, Docker, and Windows)</span></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>QUALIFICATIONS:</strong> Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, Management Information Systems, Developement or related field.<br>EXPERIENCE:<br>• Strong in integration areas, based on Restful API, exchange DB or other approach<br>• Strong MSMQ, RabbitMQ, or similar queue processing system<br>• Familiar with Microservices model<br>• Strong in SQL Server program (3 years)<br>• Familiar with .Net technology<br>• Strong in program language (C#, TSQL, JSON, XML, …)<br>• Knowledge of business processes are required.<br>• Ability to participate in and facilitate group meetings.<br><br><strong>COMPETENCIES:</strong><br>• Good performance to act within given boundaries<br>• Communications and empathy<br>• Assist in managing internal relationships and partnerships<br>• Attitude and appearance appropriate for a business office are to be maintained.<br>• Demonstrates cultural competence and behaviours consistent with the core values, vision, and mission</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Annual Health Check, Year End Party: once per year</li>\n<li>Company Trip, Team Building, Family Day: twice per year</li>\n<li>Health Insurance (Generali care 24/24 Insurance)</li>\n<li>Birthday Gift, Staff Gift</li>\n<li>Free parking batch</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "sun-life-vietnam-insurance-company-limited", "job_name": "[Hybrid] - Data Developer - AWS (Database/SQL/Python)", "tag_list": "\nDatabase\n\n\nPython\n\n\nSQL\n", "location": "LIM Tower 3, 29 A Nguyen Dinh Chieu, Da Kao Ward,, District 1, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>Job Purpose  </strong></p><p>As the part of Data developer, you will responsible for:</p><ul>\n<li>Maintain and design relational databases to support enterprise application and physical data modelling according to project requirements for data acquisition and security as well as customer-defined deliverables.</li>\n<li>Develop strategies for data modeling, design and implementation to meet stated requirements for Metadata management, Operation Data Stores, Data Lake, Data Warehouse, Data Marts and Extract Transform Load environments in batch processing and real-time injection.</li>\n<li>Create and test physical data models for a variety of business data, applications, database structures and metadata tables to meet operational goals for performance and efficiency </li>\n<li>Carrying out day-to-day support for reporting system.</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Major Accountabilities </strong></p><ol>\n<li>Produce Technical Specification documentation for the assigned works</li>\n<li>Take part in designing, coding and testing database</li>\n<li>Manage delivery of tasks within a given timeline</li>\n<li>Support other tasks as required by supervisor.</li>\n<li>Review and interpret ongoing business report requirements</li>\n<li>Build appropriate and useful reporting deliverables</li>\n<li>Provide timely scheduled management reporting</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>Technical skills</strong>:</p><ul>\n<li>Proficient<span> </span>with some of the modern relational databases such as Oracle, DB2, and SQL Server</li>\n<li>Hand-on experiences on designing and developing ETL solution by using SSIS or other ETL tools</li>\n<li>Strong in writing T-SQL, PL/SQL</li>\n<li>Good understanding of Data Modelling, processing and warehouse techniques </li>\n<li>Skilled at optimizing large complicated SQL statements</li>\n<li>Capable of troubleshooting common database issues</li>\n<li>Knowledge at reporting development with Microsoft SSIS and SSRS</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Soft skills</strong>: </p><ul>\n<li>Analytical thinking</li>\n<li>Good interpersonal and communication skills</li>\n<li>Time management</li>\n<li>Planning</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Education</strong>: University or College degree in IT or equivalent.</p><p><strong>Experience</strong>: at least 02 years of experience in Data Developer.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>- Professional working environment.<br>- Healthcare and wellness programs.<br>- Internal and external training courses.</p>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "de-heus-asia", "job_name": "Senior Database Specialist (Azure/MSSQL) - New HC", "tag_list": "\nAzure\n\n\nDatabase\n\n\nSQL\n\n\nFresher Accepted\n", "location": "Tòa nhà Sofic, 10 Đường Mai Chí Thọ, Quận 2, Thu Duc City, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Professional & global working environment\nLots of training & development opportunities\n Health-care insurances by international provider", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>JOB PURPOSE</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Support to develop and maintain MS SQL Databases and Data Warehouse within De Heus applications and Data Lake; as well as Support to manage and ensure that all databases are highly available, with proper backup &amp; recovery strategy</li>\n<li>Support to ensure all database back-end activities of Developer team (internal Dev team and out-source Dev team) work properly</li>\n<li>Support Data Analitics team to build 1 back-end data lake for De Heus Asia, which can serve Vietnam, Cambodia, Myanmar, Indonesia and can be extended further per requirement</li>\n</ul><p><strong>KEY ACTIVITIES</strong></p><p><strong>Develop, maintain, monitor and improve system</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Support to administering MS SQL Server 2014 and higher version</li>\n<li>Support to instalL, maintain &amp; monitor MS SQL Server instances</li>\n<li>Support to managing system/database security</li>\n<li>Support to configure and maintain database backups strategy &amp; disaster recovery</li>\n<li>Implement and manage high availability solutions (database replication, database mirroring, log shipping)</li>\n<li>Optimizing database performance (optimizing queries, database tuning)</li>\n<li>Provide troubleshooting &amp; technical service desk requirements </li>\n<li>Support to ensure effective support is in place for all aspects of the database management</li>\n<li>Support to ensure incident management protocols and process are effectively and consistently followed</li>\n<li>Support to ensure required high availability of MS Database </li>\n<li>Support to ensure existing database supports for business requirements </li>\n<li>Support to ensure high quality on time completion of all database projects</li>\n<li>Support to ensure proactive planning to ensure database effectively supports De Heus growth and business goals and objectives </li>\n<li>Automating administrative tasks (Integration Services)</li>\n<li>Database programming (triggers, procedures, functions)</li>\n<li>Creating reports with Crystal Reports and Reporting Services,</li>\n<li>Good knowledge about ERP, DW &amp; LAA</li>\n<li>Managing access and security</li>\n<li>Implementing required reports</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Develop, maintain, backup and restore database of local applications</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Implement and manage high availability solutions (database replication, database mirroring, log shipping)</li>\n<li>Support to ensure required high availability of MS Database </li>\n<li>Automating administrative tasks (Integration Services)</li>\n<li>Database programming (triggers, procedures, functions)</li>\n<li>Managing access and security</li>\n<li>Support developer team for database review, build and optimize from design phase to operational phase</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Create, maintain, optimize database for datalake and data warehouse</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Implement and manage high availability solutions (database replication, database mirroring, log shipping)</li>\n<li>Support to ensure required high availability of MS Database </li>\n<li>Automating administrative tasks (Integration Services)</li>\n<li>Database programming (triggers, procedures, functions)</li>\n<li>Using SQL server technologies, service and databases for creating data lake, data warehouse together with Data Engineer team</li>\n<li>Optimize query script to improve performance of server, ensure data quality and data accuracy</li>\n<li>Manage access of users (both application users and technical users) to any data table, data cube, database and and data warehouse both for on-premise and cloud</li>\n<li>Regularly check database performance, optimize data usage and data processing to have better cost of ms. Azure.</li>\n<li>Maintain the right balance of data storage and data processing in between on-premise and cloud</li>\n</ul><p><strong>RESULT</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Ensure system can work smoothly</li>\n<li>Guarantee database highly available, file backup always ready for restoring task.</li>\n<li>Provide right access to De Heus systems</li>\n<li>Ensure system can work smoothly</li>\n<li>Guarantee database highly available, file backup always ready for restoring task.</li>\n<li>Provide right access to De Heus local systems</li>\n<li>Databases of application which build by local team/outsource team work properly</li>\n<li>Datalake and data warehouse work properly</li>\n<li>Report and dashboard</li>\n<li>Database governance prototypes and procedure (who do what by when) </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Bachelor degree or equivalent in related system database areas</li>\n<li>Ms. Azure fundamental certificate, Ms. Azure SQL database &amp; service certificate </li>\n</ul><p><strong>Experience:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Minimum 3 years experience in successfully supporting/managing database in a multinational organization. Fresher with high competence can be considered. </li>\n<li>Hands on experience on Azure operation, Azure Data Factory, Azure Blob storage, Data Lake and data warehousing</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Competencies:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Strong understanding of database structures, theories, principles, and practices</li>\n<li>Working technical experience with designing, building, installing, configuring, and supporting database servers, particularly Microsoft SQL Server.</li>\n<li>Familiarity with SQL query nomenclature and fundamentals.</li>\n<li>Experience with Visual Studio and/or SSIS is a plus</li>\n<li>MCDBA certification is a plus</li>\n<li>Hands-on database tuning and troubleshooting experience.</li>\n<li>Good verbal and written communication skills (reading, writing, listening, oral, presentation)</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Language(s)</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Proficiency in English.</li>\n<li>Effective communication in Vietnamese</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Other Requirements:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Problem-solving and good analytical skills</li>\n<li>Communication, teamwork and negotiation skills</li>\n<li>Self-motivated; Proven record for actively soliciting feedback, continuous learning and self-development.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Annual Health Check, Year End Party: once per year</li>\n<li>Company Trip, Team Building, Family Day: twice per year</li>\n<li>Health Insurance (Generali care 24/24 Insurance)</li>\n<li>Birthday Gift, Staff Gift</li>\n<li>Free parking batch</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
