amp; Angular, familiar with AWS services: Lambda, Step functions, DynamoDB, SNS, SQS…</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Soft skills</strong>: </p><ul>\n<li>Problem solving</li>\n<li>Analytical thinking</li>\n<li>Time management</li>\n<li>Planning</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Education and experience</strong></p><ol>\n<li>University or College degree in IT or equivalent.</li>\n<li>Experience: At least 3 years in Java Development is required</li>\n<li>Conversation English</li>\n</ol><p><strong>Communication scope</strong></p><ol>\n<li>Communicate with line manager and other team member, 80%</li>\n<li>Communicate with business user 20%</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>- Professional working environment.<br>- Healthcare and wellness programs.<br>- Internal and external training courses.</p>\n</div>"}
