{"company_name": "intelisys-aviation", "job_name": "Quality Assurance Analyst", "tag_list": "\nQA QC\n\n\nTester\n\n\nBusiness Analyst\n", "location": "Room 804, 8th Floor, Toa nha Ha Do Airport, 02 Hong Ha, Ward 2, Tan Binh, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Highly paid and competitive salary package\nOpportunity to work on-site in Canada\nInternational and flexible working environment", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>Quality Assurance Analyst – Ho Chi Minh City</strong></p><p><span>InteliSys Aviation Systems, with headquarters in Canada and a local office in Ho Chi Minh City, is an established leader in airline passenger reservation and cargo management software with their ameliaRES and ameliaCARGO products. InteliSys’ software is used by more than 40 airlines worldwide. InteliSys is looking for great people to join our team in Ho Chi Minh City.</span></p><p><span>If you are a smart, hardworking person looking to join a great worldwide company, potential travel to Canada and grow your career, please read below, and apply today.</span></p><p><span><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></span></p><p><span>We are looking for a hands-on Manual QA to join our team. The right candidate should have an excellent track record in maintaining strong overall quality control of products adhering to reliability, performance and customer expectation.</span></p><p><span>We require a person with excellent English and Vietnamese verbal and written communication skills.</span></p><p><strong>DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Being a team player</li>\n<li>Reading and comprehending detailed technical documentation to:<ul>\n<li>Author new, and expand on existing, feature documents. Strong writing skills are required</li>\n<li>Formulate detailed test plans - both automated and manual</li>\n<li>Create demo videos for training purposes</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Collaborating with Business Analysts, Product Management, Developers, and other team members to<br>ensure delivery of high-quality software</li>\n<li>Execution of manual test cases</li>\n<li>Following a rigorous software development process to deliver the highest quality software</li>\n<li>Potential to work on automation of test cases</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Formal QA and/or BA methodology</li>\n<li>RESTful API testing (both manual and automated)<ul>\n<li>Experience with Postman</li>\n<li>ASP.NET Web API 2 experience is desirable, but not required</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Automated testing frameworks (GUI/web) would be an asset but is not required<ul><li>Protractor, Selenium, Mocha</li></ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>COMPENSATION AND BENEFITS</strong></p><ul>\n<li><span>Highly paid and competitive salary package, 13th month salary.</span></li>\n<li><span>Potential bonuses based on both company and individual performances</span></li>\n<li><span>12 days of annual leave and 05 days of sick leave</span></li>\n<li><span>Healthcare, parking, telephone, bank allowances provided</span></li>\n<li><span>100 USD for annual health-check</span></li>\n<li><span>Annual gift on your work anniversary</span></li>\n<li><span>Professional growth with individual career path</span></li>\n<li><span>Opportunity to work on-site in Canada</span></li>\n<li><span>Flexible working time</span></li>\n<li><span>Regular company sponsored outings and trips</span></li>\n</ul><p><span>We have big expectations for ourselves. We need people like you to help bring out the best in us and we promise to help bring out the best in you. Along the way, we will have fun, be stressed, argue, struggle, overcome, go on adventures, enjoy a few beverages, ponder the meaning of life amongst other things.</span></p>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "intelisys-aviation", "job_name": "Senior Angular Developer", "tag_list": "\nAngular\n\n\nNodeJS\n\n\nTypeScript\n", "location": "Room 804, 8th Floor, Toa nha Ha Do Airport, 02 Hong Ha, Ward 2, Tan Binh, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Highly paid and competitive salary package\nOpportunity to work on-site in Canada\nInternational and flexible working environment", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span><strong>About InteliSys </strong></span></p><p><span>InteliSys Aviation Systems, with headquarters in Canada and a local office in Ho Chi Minh City, is an established leader in airline passenger reservation and cargo management software with their ameliaRES and ameliaCARGO products. InteliSys’ software is used by more than 40 airlines worldwide. InteliSys is looking for great people to join our team in Ho Chi Minh City. </span></p><p><span>If you are a smart, hardworking person looking to join a great worldwide company, potential travel to Canada and grow your career, please read below, and apply today.</span></p><p><span><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION </strong></span></p><p><span>We are looking for a hands-on Angular App Developer to join our team. The right candidate should have an excellent track record in development and design exceeding timelines and expectations. </span></p><p><span>We require a person with excellent English and Vietnamese verbal and written communication skills. Those skills must complement an ability to simplify complex functional and technical requirements</span></p><p><strong>DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES</strong> </p><ul>\n<li>Design, code, test, debug and document software and business components.</li>\n<li>Optimize applications for maximum speed and availability.</li>\n<li>Write clear, concise, and well documented code.</li>\n<li>Strong focus on creating amazing user experiences.</li>\n<li>Effectively manage timelines and expectations.</li>\n<li>Reading and comprehending functional and technical specifications.</li>\n<li>Collaborating with Business Analysts, Quality Assurance Analysts, and other Developers to ensure that best practices and all established processes are followed when implementing solutions.</li>\n<li>‘Digging in’ to investigate bugs and to offer solutions.</li>\n<li><span>Following a rigorous software development process to deliver high-quality software solutions</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>from 4 years total front-end development experience. </li>\n<li>At least 2 years of deep, hands-on Angular development experience <strong>OR</strong> <span>2 years deep hands-on development experience with another SPA technology (e.g. React.js, Vue) + 1 year of Angular experience.</span>\n</li>\n<li>Your Angular knowledge should be current. </li>\n<li>Deep understanding of how to optimize Angular application for iOS and Android, including offline storage, threading, and performance tuning. </li>\n<li><span>Experience working on at least two high-volume production systems</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>COMPENSATION AND BENEFITS</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Highly paid and competitive salary package, 13th month salary.</li>\n<li>Potential bonuses based on both company and individual performances</li>\n<li>12 days of annual leave and 05 days of sick leave</li>\n<li>Healthcare, parking, telephone, bank allowances provided</li>\n<li>100 USD for annual health-check</li>\n<li>Annual gift on your work anniversary</li>\n<li>Professional growth with individual career path</li>\n<li>Opportunity to work on-site in Canada</li>\n<li>Flexible working time</li>\n<li>Regular company sponsored outings and trips</li>\n</ul><p>We have big expectations for ourselves. We need people like you to help bring out the best in us and we promise to help bring out the best in you. Along the way, we will have fun, be stressed, argue, struggle, overcome, go on adventures, enjoy a few beverages, ponder the meaning of life amongst other things.</p>\n</div>"}
