{"company_name": "rch-asia", "job_name": "Tester Manual Android", "tag_list": "\nTester\n\n\nAndroid\n\n\nQA QC\n", "location": "PAX SKY, 13 Truong Dinh, Vo Thi Sau Ward, District 3, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Additional Private Insurance \nDaily Supply of Fruits, Drink \n13th Month Salary & Bonus", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>RCH develops, produces and commercializes Electronic Cash Registers (ECRs), Point of Sales (PoS) and cloud services for Food&amp;Beverage and Retail markets in Italy and EU countries. These products and services are constantly evolving to both comply with new fiscal legislation in the different countries and offer effective, appealing and on-the-cutting-edge user experience to our final customers. To consolidate and expand its Research and Development office, RCH is looking for Test Engineers at different level of experience. </p><p>The candidates shall play a key role in our Software Validation and Verification by: </p><p>1. Identifying critical operational areas and use cases of RCH products and services based on the new functionalities that shall be implemented </p><p>2. Define test plans to verify and validate the correct implementation of these use cases in all potential error conditions 3. Implement and execute related test cases</p><p> 4. Automate these test cases through software programs to be run within RCH continuous integration and testing environment </p><p>5. Availability to travel in Italy, Vietnam and in case to other countries inside and outside EU</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>• Can-do attitude and passion to face challenges<br>• Strong commitment to meet goals and deadlines, to learn new methods and technologies, align<br>and improve the common way of working<br>• Willing to work in Agile teams in a dynamic environment, to constantly learn and improve by<br>exiting personal comfort zone<br>• Bachelor or higher University degree<br>• Test definition and execution c