ntire software development life cycle and test cycles (Unit, Regression, Functional, Systems, Stress &amp; Scale, Smoke &amp; Sanity)</li>\n<li>Consolidated knowledge of Python or other script language for test case automation</li>\n<li>Knowledge of Object Oriented programming and related Design Patterns</li>\n<li>Knowledge of python, PHP, Javascripts</li>\n<li>Knowledge of robot framework for automation tests</li>\n<li>Knowledge of Jira, Confluence, Share point Working experience of versioning systems, in particular GIT, and continuous integration environments such as Bitbucket or others</li>\n<li>Fluent written and spoken English, possibly German and/or French</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span>CHẾ ĐỘ LƯƠNG THƯỞNG PHÚC LỢI</span><br><span>• 13th month salary (cycle: Jan – Dec. If the employee works for from 2 months to less than 6 months, he/she will be entitled to ½ 13th month salary; if the employee works for 6 months to 1 year, he/she will be entitled to a full 13th month salary);</span><br><span>• 100% salary in probation period;</span><br><span>• Subscription of the national social insurance scheme from probation (paid on gross salary);</span><br><span>• Subscription of PVI health care program after 2 months of probation;</span><br><span>• Yearly company trip;</span><br><span>• Periodic team-building activities;</span><br><span>• Yearly health examination;</span><br><span>• Transportation allowance: 20,000/working day in office;</span><br><span>• Lunch allowance: 700,000/month;</span><br><span>• Monthly attendance allowance: 400,000/month (after 2 months probation);</span><br><span>• Employee is to be given a laptop for work use.</span></p>\n</div>"}
