{"company_name": "intelisys-aviation", "job_name": "Senior Backend (.NET) Developer", "tag_list": "\nC#\n\n\nSQL\n\n\n.NET\n", "location": "Room 804, 8th Floor, Toa nha Ha Do Airport, 02 Hong Ha, Ward 2, Tan Binh, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Highly paid and competitive salary package\nOpportunity to work on-site in Canada\nInternational and flexible working environment", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span><strong>ABOUT INTELISYS </strong></span></p><p><span>InteliSys Aviation Systems, with headquarters in Canada and a local office in Ho Chi Minh, is an established leader in airline passenger reservation and cargo management software with their ameliaRES and ameliaCARGO products. InteliSys’ software is in use by more than 40 airlines worldwide and are looking for great people to join our team in Ho Chi Minh. </span></p><p><span>If you are a smart hardworking person looking to join a great worldwide company, travel to Canada and grow your career, please read below and apply </span></p><p> </p><p><span><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></span></p><p>We are looking for a Senior Backend Developer with a concentration on Web and API technologies, to join our team. The right candidate should have an excellent track record in development and design exceeding timelines and expectations.  </p><p>We require a person with excellent verbal and written communication skills in English. Those skills must compliment an ability to track down bottlenecks in operational environments and simplify complex functional and technical systems. </p><p> </p><p><strong>RESPONSIBILITIES:</strong> </p><ul>\n<li>Design, code, test, debug and document software, including web technologies and business components. </li>\n<li>Reading and comprehending functional and technical specifications </li>\n<li>Collaborating with Business Analysts, Quality Assurance Analysts, and other Developers to ensure that best practices and all processes are followed when implementing solutions </li>\n<li>‘Digging in’ to investigate bugs and to offer solutions </li>\n<li><span>Following a rigorous software development process to deliver high-quality software solutions </span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Strong knowledge in C#, .NET, Microsoft SQL Server with at least 5 years experience. </li>\n<li>Experience with Git, deployment, unit testing, RESTful etc.</li>\n<li>A Bachelor’s degree (or equivalent experience) in Software/Computer Engineering</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>COMPENSATION AND BENEFITS</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Highly paid and competitive salary package, 13th month salary.</li>\n<li>Potential bonuses based on both company and individual performances</li>\n<li>12 days of annual leave and 05 days of sick leave</li>\n<li>Healthcare, parking, telephone, bank allowances provided</li>\n<li>100 USD for annual health-check</li>\n<li>Professional growth with individual career path</li>\n<li>Opportunity to work on-site in Canada</li>\n<li>Flexible working time</li>\n<li>Regular company sponsored outings and trips</li>\n</ul><p>We have big expectations for ourselves. We need people like you to help bring out the best in us and we promise to help bring out the best in you. Along the way, we will have fun, be stressed, argue, struggle, overcome, go on adventures, enjoy a few beverages, ponder the meaning of life amongst other things.</p>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "cong-ty-tnhh-thankslab-viet-nam", "job_name": "Game Client/Server Developer (C++)", "tag_list": "\nC++\n\n\nGames\n", "location": "Số 32 đường D5, P.25, Binh Thanh, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span>Công ty Thankslab Việt Nam cần tuyển Game Client/Server Developers (C ++) có hai năm kinh nghiệm trở lên hoặc kỹ năng tương đương.</span></p><p><span>Phát triển Application trên C ++</span><br><span>**Cụ thể sẽ trao đổi thêm trong quá trình phỏng vấn.</span><br> </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>- Cần có 2 năm kinh nghiệm theo chuyên môn.<br>- Có kinh nghiệm phát triển bằng ngôn ngữ Visual C++ (bắt buộc)／ Win32 API／ DirectX／2D, 3D Programming／MFC／TCP / IP／IOCP / Network<br>- Có tư duy về thiết kế, xây dựng hệ thống<br>- Có hiểu biết về engine game<br>- Có kinh nghiệm về NodeJS là một lợi thế.<br>- Nhiệt huyết, chủ động, sáng tạo trong công việc, có khả năng chịu áp lực công việc cao.<br>- Có khả năng nắm bắt, tự học hỏi và nghiên cứu kỹ thuật &amp; công nghệ mới<br>- Tư duy logic, xử lý vấn đề &amp; thuật toán tốt<br>- Có khả năng làm việc độc lập và làm việc nhóm, ham học hỏi</p><p>Ưu tiên<br>- Người có kinh nghiệm, có khả năng giao tiếp một trong các ngôn ngữ: Anh, Nhật, Hàn.<br>- Người sử dụng, đọc hiểu tốt các tài liệu kỹ thuật tiếng Anh.<br><br> </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Tham gia BHXH full lương theo yêu cầu</li>\n<li>Chế độ lương tháng 13</li>\n<li>Review lương định kỳ</li>\n<li>Môi trường làm việc chuyên nghiệp, cởi mở, hòa đồng và thân thiện</li>\n<li>Du lịch và party định kỳ (Noel, Halloween, Tiệc cuối năm)</li>\n<li>Nghỉ trưa relax 1.5 tiếng</li>\n<li>Đuợc trang bị hai màn hình và có cơ hội tiếp xúc với các thiết bị hiện đại</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "cong-ty-tnhh-thankslab-viet-nam", "job_name": "3D Modelers ", "tag_list": "\nDesigner\n\n\nGames\n", "location": "Số 32 đường D5, P.25, Binh Thanh, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Model phối cảnh, trãi UV, vẽ Texture theo yêu cầu. Set up (skin, rig, bone) nhân vật và đồ vật.</li>\n<li>Tạo bối cảnh, nhân vật, trang phục, phụ hiện, nội thất...</li>\n<li>Thực hiện các yêu cầu công việc khác theo chỉ đạo cấp trên.</li>\n<li>Số lượng: 02 người</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Có kinh nghiệm về Modeling + UV + Texturing</li>\n<li>Thành thạo 3D Max (biết Maya là một lợi thế). Sử dụng tốt Photoshop</li>\n<li>Có kinh nghiệm tạo hình 3D (bối cảnh, nhân vật, trang phục, phụ kiện, nội thất...)</li>\n<li>Hand Paint hoặc Real Style</li>\n<li>Hiểu các tài liệu đặc tả kỹ thuật và điều chỉnh dữ liệu 3D theo yêu cầu.</li>\n</ul><p><i><strong>Ưu tiên nếu có kinh nghiệm sau:</strong></i></p><ul>\n<li>Zbrush, Substance Painter, Unity, Unreal Engine</li>\n<li>Chuyển data từ high polygons sang low polygons</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Tham gia BHXH full lương theo yêu cầu</li>\n<li>Chế độ lương tháng 13</li>\n<li>Review lương định kỳ</li>\n<li>Môi trường làm việc chuyên nghiệp, cởi mở, hòa đồng và thân thiện</li>\n<li>Du lịch và party định kỳ (Noel, Halloween, Tiệc cuối năm)</li>\n<li>Nghỉ trưa relax 1.5 tiếng</li>\n<li>Đuợc trang bị hai màn hình và có cơ hội tiếp xúc với các thiết bị hiện đại</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "saigon-south-international-school", "job_name": "Systems Engineer/Cyber Security Specialist ", "tag_list": "\nSystem Engineer\n\n\nLinux\n\n\nEnglish\n", "location": "78 Nguyen Duc Canh, District 7, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "International working environment\nCompetitive salary and benefits\nUp to 26 leave days per year", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>A – Job Summary </strong></p><p>We are seeking a System Engineer/Security Specialist to be responsible for protecting our school’s computer systems and networks from cyber threats. The System Engineer/Security Specialist will be responsible for the installation, monitoring, maintenance, and support of the school’s security measures, in addition to providing technical guidance and direction to the IT team. </p><p>The System Engineer/Security Specialist should have strong knowledge of defensive Cybersecurity in a large environment and a good working knowledge of Tenable and Nessus. The successful candidate must also have a good working knowledge of Linux and Windows operating systems, be proficient in scripting in both Linux and Windows, and have experience with Active Directory.</p><p><strong>B – Essential duties and responsibilities </strong></p><p>• Install, configure, and maintain security measures to protect our school’s computer systems and networks from cyber threats.</p><p>• Monitor and maintain the school’s security systems such as Tenable and Nessus.</p><p>• Troubleshoot and resolve technical issues related to computer systems and networks.</p><p>• Configure and maintain network hardware such as routers, switches, and wireless access points.</p><p>• Manage user accounts and ensure that users have proper access to the systems and networks.</p><p>• Ensure the security of the school’s computer systems and networks.</p><p>• Monitor, maintain, and configure virtualized environments using Linux and Windows operating systems.</p><p>• Perform routine maintenance and software upgrades.</p><p>• Create and maintain detailed documentation of the security systems and networks.</p><p>• Respond to user inquiries and requests for technical support.</p><p>• Provide technical guidance and direction to the IT team.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>• Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, Information Technology, or related field. </p><p>• 5+ years of experience working with computer systems and networks. </p><p>• Knowledge of Cybersecurity and a good working knowledge of Tenable. </p><p>• Proficiency with Linux and Windows operating systems. </p><p>• Proficiency in scripting in both Linux and Windows. </p><p>• Experience with Active Directory. </p><p>• Excellent problem-solving and troubleshooting skills. </p><p>• Ability to work independently and as part of a team. </p><p>• Highly organized and detail-oriented. </p><p>• Excellent English communication and customer service skills.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Competitive salary and benefits (Health care, PD, Fitness, Swimming Pool, Travel Trip, Long Service Award, Annual Health Check, Football Club, Badminton Club,...)</li>\n<li>Western Environment; Friendly Colleagues and Nice Boss</li>\n<li>Excellent opportunity for seasoned Programmer</li>\n<li>Up to 26 leave days per year</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "saigon-south-international-school", "job_name": "Database & Systems Specialist (SQL, JavaScript, Python)", "tag_list": "\nDatabase\n\n\nSQL\n\n\nJavaScript\n", "location": "78 Nguyen Duc Canh, District 7, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "International working environment\nCompetitive salary and benefits\nUp to 26 leave days per year", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>A – Job summary</strong></p><p>The Database and Systems Specialist will support the school with connecting all custom and purchased programs insuring that the right data is available to the end user at all times.</p><p><strong>B – Essential duties and responsibilities </strong></p><p><span>The responsibilities of the programmer include:</span></p><ol>\n<li>Manage and maintain our collection of SQL based databases</li>\n<li>Insure connectivity with Active Directory and Google</li>\n<li>Support data flow to and from on premise and cloud based solutions using APIs</li>\n<li>Stay abreast with <span>current</span> database technology, web frameworks and API technology</li>\n<li>\n<span>Provide u</span>ser support <span>for</span> developed applications.</li>\n<li>Undergo training to <span>constantly</span> improve <span>their</span> skill base.</li>\n<li>Work with the <span>IT Director </span>to establish goals and objectives to improve the quality of service provided.</li>\n<li>Attend technology department meetings when requested.</li>\n<li>Carry out any other duties as assigned by the ICT Director.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Knowledge, Education and Experience:</strong><ul>\n<li>\n<span>Database </span>Development and integration<span> (MS SQL, MySQL/MariaDB, </span>Postgres<span>, Oracle, </span>Json<span>, ODBC)</span>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span>Basic Web Application Development             </span><ul>\n<li><span>Front-end: Javascript, JQuery, ReactJS, Flux, CSS, HTML </span></li>\n<li><span>Back-end: Python, PHP</span></li>\n<li><span>CMS: Django, WordPress, Joomla or similar</span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Basic understanding of Version<span> Control Software (GIT, Gitlab)</span>\n</li>\n<li>Tools/Platforms: Active Directory, Nginix, Docker, Docker Builder, Shell/Bash scripting, Powershell.</li>\n<li>\n<span>Operating System: Mac</span>OS<span>/Linux</span>\n</li>\n<li><span>Python 3.x fluency</span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Skills:</strong><ul><li><span>Good at oral and written English</span></li></ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Abilities:</strong><ul>\n<li><span>Work well with people</span></li>\n<li><span>A dedication to continually update knowledge</span></li>\n<li><span>Able to explain technical problems in simple terms</span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Competitive salary and benefits (Health care, PD, Fitness, Swimming Pool, Travel Trip, Long Service Award, Annual Health Check, Football Club, Badminton Club,...)</li>\n<li>Western Environment; Friendly Colleagues and Nice Boss</li>\n<li>Excellent opportunity for seasoned Programmer</li>\n<li>Up to 26 leave days per year</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "cong-ty-tnhh-thankslab-viet-nam", "job_name": "Bridge Software Engineer (BrSE)", "tag_list": "\nBridge Engineer\n\n\nJapanese\n\n\nQA QC\n", "location": "Số 32 đường D5, P.25, Binh Thanh, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li><span>Quản lý dự án: lập kế hoạch, theo dõi tiến độ, quản lý nhóm </span></li>\n<li><span>Làm việc với chuyên gia phát triển phần mềm </span></li>\n<li><span>Giao tiếp, trao đổi, nhận, phân tích các yêu cầu của dự án phần mềm từ công ty mẹ và truyền đạt cho đội dự án Việt Nam</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li><span>Có kinh nghiệm làm BrSE từ 2 năm trở lên đối với Junior và 3 năm trở lên đối với Middle </span></li>\n<li><span>Có kinh nghiệm quản lý dự án </span></li>\n<li><span>Có kinh nghiệm làm việc với chuyên gia phát triển phần mềm </span></li>\n<li><span>Tiếng Nhật N2 trở lên </span></li>\n<li><span>Có kinh nghiệm đánh giá Code và QA là một lợi thế </span></li>\n<li><span>Có kinh nghiệm làm tài liệu đặc tả kĩ thuật cho khách hàng và kĩ sư là một lợi thế </span></li>\n<li><span>Tuổi từ 25~35</span></li>\n</ul><p>***Ưu tiên:</p><ul>\n<li>Có kinh nghiệm phát triển Web</li>\n<li>Có kinh nghiệm về PHP (front-end, back-end)</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Tham gia BHXH full lương theo yêu cầu</li>\n<li>Chế độ lương tháng 13</li>\n<li>Review lương định kỳ</li>\n<li>Môi trường làm việc chuyên nghiệp, cởi mở, hòa đồng và thân thiện</li>\n<li>Du lịch và party định kỳ (Noel, Halloween, Tiệc cuối năm)</li>\n<li>Nghỉ trưa relax 1.5 tiếng</li>\n<li>Đuợc trang bị hai màn hình và có cơ hội tiếp xúc với các thiết bị hiện đại</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "saigon-south-international-school", "job_name": "System Administrator (System Admin, Linux, English)", "tag_list": "\nSystem Admin\n\n\nLinux\n\n\nEnglish\n", "location": "78 Nguyen Duc Canh, District 7, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "International working environment\nCompetitive salary and benefits\nUp to 26 leave days per year", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>A – Job Summary </strong></p><p><span>We are seeking a Junior System Administrator to assist with the installation, maintenance, and support of our school’s computer systems, networks, and related hardware and software. The Junior System Administrator will work closely with the IT team to ensure our school’s network and computers are running smoothly.   </span></p><p><span>The Junior System Administrator should have a good working knowledge of Google Apps and virtualization technologies such as VMWare and Veeam. The successful candidate must also be highly organized and have excellent English communication skills.</span></p><p><strong>B – Essential duties and responsibilities </strong></p><ol>\n<li><span>Install, configure, and maintain Windows, Mac, and Linux operating systems </span></li>\n<li><span>Troubleshoot and resolve technical issues related to computer systems and networks. </span></li>\n<li><span>Configure and maintain network hardware such as routers, switches, and wireless access points. • Ensure the security of the school’s computer systems and networks. </span></li>\n<li><span>Monitor and maintain the school’s Google Apps environment.</span></li>\n<li><span>Monitor, maintain, and configure virtualized environments using VMWare and Veeam. </span></li>\n<li><span>Ensure that all software is up-to date and properly licensed. </span></li>\n<li><span>Respond to user inquiries and requests for technical support. </span></li>\n<li><span>Perform routine maintenance and software upgrades. </span></li>\n<li><span>Manage user accounts and ensure that users have proper access to the systems and networks. </span></li>\n<li><span>Create and maintain detailed documentation of the network and systems.</span></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li><span>Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, Information Technology, or related field. </span></li>\n<li><span>3+ years of experience working with computer systems, networks, and related hardware and software. </span></li>\n<li><span>Proficiency with Windows, Mac, and Linux operating systems. </span></li>\n<li><span>Good working knowledge of Google Apps and virtualization technologies such as VMWare and Veeam. </span></li>\n<li><span>Excellent problem-solving and troubleshooting skills. </span></li>\n<li><span>Ability to work independently and as part of a team. </span></li>\n<li><span>Highly organized and detail-oriented. </span></li>\n<li><span>Excellent English communication and customer service skills.</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Competitive salary and benefits (Health care, PD, Fitness, Swimming Pool, Travel Trip, Long Service Award, Annual Health Check, Football Club, Badminton Club,...)</li>\n<li>Western Environment; Friendly Colleagues and Nice Boss</li>\n<li>Excellent opportunity for seasoned Programmer</li>\n<li>Up to 26 leave days per year</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "gene-solutions", "job_name": "IT Security ", "tag_list": "\nNetworking\n\n\nSystem Engineer\n\n\nDevOps\n", "location": "366 Nguyễn Trãi, District 5, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><i>Gene Solutions is a leading company in Vietnam specializing in the research, development and application of the most advanced genetic tests, providing genetic testing services for screening, diagnosis and treatment orientation.</i> </p><p><i>Over the years, Gene Solutions has continuously developed and invested in building a strong and excellent R&amp;D team, focusing on research and application of useful technologies that have been certified in the world to bring latest genetic testing and services, with the best quality at the most affordable cost, increasing Vietnamese people's access to essential genetic tests for prevention, examination and treatment, improving the quality of medical examination and treatment, contributing to the quality of medical services and health for the community.</i> </p><p><strong>RESPONSIBILITIES </strong></p><ul>\n<li>Review, develop &amp; implement IT policies, controls, and procedures.  </li>\n<li>Review, monitor data backup/restore instruction documents and DRP from related departments. </li>\n<li>Establish, observational awareness, and conduct periodic checks according to the IT policy. </li>\n<li>Perform security assessment scans and monitor identified security patches to ensure stable IT system operation. </li>\n<li>Co-ordinate with IT and business to ensure the user access control is performed well.  </li>\n<li>Coordinate with external and internal audit. </li>\n<li>Other tasks related to information security. </li>\n</ul><p> </p><p> </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>REQUIREMENTS </strong></p><ul>\n<li>A bachelor’s degree holder in Information Technology, Information Security related field. </li>\n<li>At least 1 year’s experiences in any of the areas listed above. </li>\n<li>Have a sense of responsibility for work, confidentiality of information, honesty, enthusiastic about learning and developing information security in healthcare. </li>\n<li>Knowledge of information security controls, guidelines, and standards, NIST, HIPAA, ISO, OWASP, … </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Discounted suitable genetic testing products offered for you and your loved ones;</li>\n<li>Healthcare insurance, plus Adoption/Fertility (IVF test) support;</li>\n<li>Shared leaves, wellness, and leadership training, and volunteer time off;</li>\n<li>Flexible working hours, casual working attire, transparent and supportive culture;</li>\n<li>And much more for you to explore with us…</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "gene-solutions", "job_name": "3+ years Fullstack Developer (.NET, C#, JavaScript) ", "tag_list": "\n.NET\n\n\nC#\n\n\nJavaScript\n", "location": "366 Nguyễn Trãi, District 5, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><i>Gene Solutions là công ty hàng đầu tại Việt Nam chuyên nghiên cứu, phát triển và ứng dụng các xét nghiệm gen tiên tiến nhất, cung cấp các dịch vụ xét nghiệm liên quan đến di truyền phục vụ sàng lọc, chẩn đoán bệnh và định hướng điều trị liên quan đến gen.</i></p><p><i>Trong những năm qua, Gene Solutions có những bước phát triển và không ngừng đầu tư xây dựng đội ngũ R&amp;D mạnh và xuất sắc, tập trung nghiên cứu và ứng dụng những công nghệ hữu ích đã được chứng nhận trên thế giới nhằm mang đến các xét nghiệm gen mới nhất với chất lượng tốt nhất và chi phí hợp lý nhất, tăng khả năng tiếp cận của người Việt Nam tới những xét nghiệm di truyền thiết yếu phục vụ cho việc phòng, khám và chữa bệnh, nâng tầm chất lượng khám chữa bệnh, đóng góp vào công cuộc nâng cao chất lượng dịch vụ y tế và sức khỏe cho cộng đồng.</i></p><p>Vị trí Fullstack Developer này sẽ chịu trách nhiệm cho việc xây dựng và bảo trì các phần mềm của Công ty.</p><ul>\n<li>Phát triển các hệ thống phần mềm theo yêu cầu của công ty</li>\n<li>Hỗ trợ và fix lỗi sản phẩm trong quá trình vận hành</li>\n<li>Tích hợp các hệ thống phần mềm</li>\n<li>Nhiệm vụ khác theo sự phân công của quản lý</li>\n<li>Các công việc khác do nhu cầu phát sinh.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>Chúng tôi đang tìm kiếm một người:</p><ul>\n<li>Ít nhất <strong>03 năm kinh nghiệm</strong> full stack web development và SQL Server</li>\n<li>Frontend technical: Bootstrap, Jquery, html, html5, Vuejs, Ajax,..</li>\n<li>Backend technical: API, C#, MVC, Entity Framework</li>\n<li>Database: SQL Server, Store procedure, Function, View</li>\n<li>Kinh nghiệm làm các dự án phần mềm theo mô hình Scrum</li>\n<li>Kinh nghiệm và kĩ năng unit test</li>\n<li>Có tư duy logic tốt, xử lý tình huống linh hoạt, kỹ năng giao tiếp, kỹ năng giải quyết vấn đề</li>\n<li>Cần cù, siêng năng, khả năng làm việc với cường độ cao</li>\n<li>Có trách nhiệm và đam mê với công việc</li>\n<li>Có khả năng sắp xếp, lập kế hoạch quỹ thời gian công việc</li>\n<li>Có kinh nghiệm sử dụng Github để quản lý Source code</li>\n<li>Ưu tiên ứng viên có kinh nghiệm trong lĩnh vực y tế, xét nghiệm</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Lương tháng 13</li>\n<li>Bảo hiểm y tế tư nhân</li>\n<li>Vouchers, quà vào các dịp đặc biệt </li>\n<li>Nghỉ Lễ Tết, phép năm đầy đủ theo đúng quy định của Nhà nước.</li>\n<li>Tham gia tất cả các bảo hiểm (BHXH, BHYT, BHTN), được hưởng đầy đủ chính sách, chế độ theo Luật lao động.</li>\n<li>Mô trường làm việc năng động, nhân văn.</li>\n<li>Du lịch thường niên.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "qorvo", "job_name": "Embedded Firmware Engineer ", "tag_list": "\nEmbedded\n\n\nC#\n\n\nC language\n", "location": "5th Floor, CIC Tower - 219 Trung Kinh Street, Cau Giay, Ha Noi", "three_reasons": "Dynamic, technological, global, and Agile working \nFlexible working arrangement \n13 months of salary, bonus paid twice a year and m", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>As an Embedded Firmware Engineer at Qorvo Vietnam, you will play a vital role in supporting the life cycle of an entire range of products right from its inception to the final implementation of the software application.<br>You will conduct a proper analysis to design and develop firmware, so as to provide the best services for the clients’ products. Before implementing the firmware, you must ensure that it is tested properly and collaborates with the other engineering staff to address the technical issues and resolve them. After the proper implementation of the system, you will evaluate the performance of the system and ensure that it is compliant with the company's rules and regulations.</p><ul>\n<li>Perform digital design IC verification to ensure that it is running and operating smoothly.</li>\n<li>Post-silicon bench evaluation and characterization</li>\n<li>Embedded firmware design (control applications: power, motor; serial communications, device drivers, etc.)</li>\n<li>Create and maintain firmware documentation </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>A minimum of a Bachelor’s degree in Computer Engineering, Electrical Engineering, Computer Science or related degree is required for this position.</li>\n<li>Have experience with MCU or DSP embedded design and software tools (IDE): IAR EWARM, Keil uVision, Eclipse.</li>\n<li>Good at hardware PCB design with Altium, labworks.</li>\n<li>Have hands-on experience in Power Conversion, Motor Control and Basic control theory knowledge.</li>\n<li>Solid knowledge and experience with Version Control Systems (VCS): GIT, etc.</li>\n<li>Good knowledge at ARM Cortex-M architecture. MCU/DSP Peripherals (Timer/PWM, ADC, DAC, UART) experience is a plus.</li>\n<li>Have intense experience with Assembly and .NET Framework in C# is a plus.</li>\n<li>Demonstrated ability on mixed-signal firmware and system design, good experience with Matlab and Simulink is an advantage.</li>\n<li>Good time-management skills with the ability to multi-task and collaborate with cross-team on multiple projects.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li><span>Dynamic, technological, global, and Agile working environment  </span></li>\n<li><span>Flexible working arrangement  </span></li>\n<li><span>Overseas travel opportunities for training and working related  </span></li>\n<li><span>Performance review to adjust salary and title/position.  </span></li>\n<li><span>13 months of salary, bonus paid twice a year and many other side benefits such as lunch allowance, healthcare program, annual health-screen, sport activities, gifts on special occasions  </span></li>\n</ul><p> </p>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "qorvo", "job_name": "IC Test Development Engineer (C/C++)", "tag_list": "\nC++\n\n\nEnglish\n\n\nC language\n", "location": "5th Floor, CIC Tower - 219 Trung Kinh Street, Cau Giay, Ha Noi", "three_reasons": "Dynamic, technological, global, and Agile working \nFlexible working arrangement \n13 months of salary, bonus paid twice a year and m", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>SUMMARY:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Design test solution for both RD debugging and production test release.</li>\n<li>Work on yield improvement and test time reduction, etc..</li>\n<li>Response to customer return case, support AE/QE to analyze failure with ATE test data.</li>\n<li>Support RD/QE for BI, ESD data analysis.</li>\n<li>Experience in multi-site test programming, tester platform conversion. </li>\n<li>Hardware design with Altium software.</li>\n</ul><p><strong>RESPONSIBILITIES:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>DFT review with designers to optimize test method.</li>\n<li>Program coding generate, debugging &amp; releasing.</li>\n<li>ATE evaluation report with yield, bin summary, distribution analysis &amp; full temp test.</li>\n<li>Subcon sustaining for low yield &amp; Test related issues.</li>\n<li>ATE support for FA case to analyze failure with ATE test data.</li>\n<li>Support RD/QE for BI, ESD data test &amp; analysis.</li>\n<li>Test time reduction to lower test cost.</li>\n<li>Identify EA, participate in evaluating significant EA, and renew the corresponding info in time.</li>\n<li>Routine monitoring and checking for internal system operation.</li>\n<li>Responsible for the inspection and management of special equipment.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Strong programming skills in C/C++ or other languages.</li>\n<li>Strong hardware circuit understanding and debugging skills.</li>\n<li>Relevant work experience of at least 5 years.</li>\n<li>Bachelor or above degree.</li>\n<li>Able to use ALTIUM/PADS/PROTEL to design PCB.</li>\n<li>Nice to have: experience with ASL1K/ETS300 test platform &amp; Test theory of analog device</li>\n<li>Strong interpersonal skills, impartial and active working attitude.</li>\n<li>Good English communication skills and computer operation skills</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li><span>Dynamic, technological, global, and Agile working environment  </span></li>\n<li><span>Flexible working arrangement  </span></li>\n<li><span>Overseas travel opportunities for training and working related  </span></li>\n<li><span>Performance review to adjust salary and title/position.  </span></li>\n<li><span>13 months of salary, bonus paid twice a year and many other side benefits such as lunch allowance, healthcare program, annual health-screen, sport activities, gifts on special occasions  </span></li>\n</ul><p> </p>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "wiztech-vietnam", "job_name": "HCM - Operation Manager/ Project Manager", "tag_list": "\nProject Manager\n\n\nEnglish\n\n\nManager\n", "location": "Floor 3, VVA Building, 279 Ly Tu Trong Street, Ben Thanh Ward, District 1, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Up to $4000\nCompulsory insurance full salary\nWorking in a dynamic and professional environment", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Application area - supervise the development and use of new applications, systems software, and upgrades to existing applications throughout their task.</li>\n<li>Application area - ensure that development projects match business needs and requirements or stakeholders (internal or with customers), furnish end-user requirements, identify and resolve systems issues, conduct pre-testing of systems and make proper modifications.</li>\n<li>Application area - team up with analysts, designers, and executives in the installation and testing of new software programs and applications.</li>\n<li>Application area - design, create and install enhancements and upgrades, applications software or other programs.</li>\n<li>Application/services area - conduct presales study and engagement with customer to understand the needs and provide the necessary solutions, project manage the delivery of suggested solution and implementation as well as services delivery.</li>\n<li>Services area - confer with infrastructure and cloud engineers to ensure quality assurance, algorithmic consistency in our services offering.</li>\n<li>Services area - research and make recommendations on software products and services for procurement.</li>\n<li>Services area - do feasibility studies for customer on solution and give suggestions based on findings that align with our offering in vietnam.</li>\n<li>Management area – establish the operation process and procedure for vietnam offices across hcm and hanoi.</li>\n<li>Management area - supervising team of staffs in tasks assignment and quality of delivery.</li>\n<li>Management area - providing operation plan, execution and support in all services delivered by wiztech vietnam. • management area - manage and direct procedures for the overall operation team towards their utilization for business operations. </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Management area – work closely with the general manager to establish the overall plan for the vietnam market and support the execution of the agreed plan.</li>\n<li>Management area – work closely with regional operation director to align all operation processes and procedures.</li>\n<li>Management area – overall technical resources planning and work closely with the human resource team to recruit the necessary resources to support projects and sales activities.</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Qualifications and education requirements</strong></p><ul>\n<li>A bachelor’s degree is the minimum academic requirement.</li>\n<li>Certification in agile development will be prefer but is required.</li>\n<li>Training for corporate project management (cpm) skills and/or project management professional (pmp) or any job related experience is prefer but not necessary.</li>\n<li>Good communication skill.</li>\n<li>Good understanding of managed services, security and cloud technology.</li>\n<li>Managed an effective team of developers experience will be preferred.</li>\n<li>Good team player.</li>\n<li>Fluence in conversation in english is preferred.</li>\n<li>Able to write and present in english.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span><strong>1. Working environment</strong></span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Colleagues are friendly, sociable, support together</span></li>\n<li><span>Respectful working style.</span></li>\n</ul><p><span><strong>2. Competitive benefit packages</strong></span></p><ul>\n<li><span>13th salary &amp; Bonus</span></li>\n<li><span>Attractive salary with annual salary review</span></li>\n<li><span>Holiday: 14 annual leave days for Manager based on Vietnam Government regulations.</span></li>\n<li><span>Free refreshments including coffee, tea, and snack, parking fee..</span></li>\n<li><span>Team building, monthly party (birthday party)</span></li>\n<li><span>Open culture: employee is valued, treated fairly and trusted</span></li>\n<li><span>Have opportunity to work with overseas clients, global Projects</span></li>\n<li><span>Chance to work in a friendly, well-equipped environment with both foreigners</span></li>\n<li><span>(Singaporean, Japanese, Korean, Chinese, Malaysian, Indonesian, Philippines)</span></li>\n<li><span>Opportunity to challenge with big projects in businesses fields such as: Luxury Hotel</span></li>\n<li><span>Chains, shopping mall, Manufacturing etc.</span></li>\n<li><span>Others benefits such as holidays and insurance benefits follow Vietnamese law.</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "wiztech-vietnam", "job_name": "Senior IT Support Consultant (Level 2), HCMC, Hanoi", "tag_list": "\nIT Support\n\n\nSystem Engineer\n\n\nSystem Admin\n", "location": "Floor 3, VVA Building, 279 Ly Tu Trong Street, Ben Thanh Ward, District 1, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Up to $4000\nCompulsory insurance full salary\nWorking in a dynamic and professional environment", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Takes cases from Level 1.</li>\n<li>Provides in-depth troubleshooting and backend analysis.</li>\n<li>Undertake Systems Projects.</li>\n<li>Prepare documentation.</li>\n<li>Monitor and respond quickly to incoming requests relate to IT issues from internal and customers.</li>\n<li>Maintain computer systems and act as support if any system goes down.</li>\n<li>Responsible for PC’s, Printers, Servers and related equipment (monitor, keyboard, mouse, hard drive, etc).</li>\n<li>Maintain user PCs, including upgrades and configuration as needed.</li>\n<li>Assist with onboarding of new users.</li>\n<li>Keep inventory of all equipment, software, and license users.</li>\n<li>Install, configure, and upgrade PC software.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Able to provide standby after office hours on a roster basis.</li>\n<li>Patient task managers who know how to find or create solutions to unexpected problems.</li>\n<li>Work with multiple teams and departments, and need to be able to communicate and take ownership to ensure tasks are completed appropriately and on time.</li>\n<li>General awareness of computer systems, PC repair, and network management.</li>\n<li>Resourcefulness and quick-thinking nature to troubleshoot new and critical technical issues as they arise.</li>\n<li>Ability to deploy, configure, and support operating systems on desktop and mobile.</li>\n<li>Understanding and appreciation for information security within systems and user devices.</li>\n<li>Strong drive to provide excellent customer service and experience, with an awareness of prioritization of tasks, stakeholders, budget, and time.</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Minimum Nitec/Diploma in information technology discipline.</li>\n<li>ITIL certification is an advantage.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span><strong>1. Working environment</strong></span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Colleagues are friendly, sociable, support together</span></li>\n<li><span>Respectful working style.</span></li>\n</ul><p><span><strong>2. Competitive benefit packages</strong></span></p><ul>\n<li><span>13th salary &amp; Bonus</span></li>\n<li><span>Attractive salary with annual salary review</span></li>\n<li><span>Holiday: 14 annual leave days for Manager based on Vietnam Government regulations.</span></li>\n<li><span>Free refreshments including coffee, tea, and snack, parking fee..</span></li>\n<li><span>Team building, monthly party (birthday party)</span></li>\n<li><span>Open culture: employee is valued, treated fairly and trusted</span></li>\n<li><span>Have opportunity to work with overseas clients, global Projects</span></li>\n<li><span>Chance to work in a friendly, well-equipped environment with both foreigners</span></li>\n<li><span>(Singaporean, Japanese, Korean, Chinese, Malaysian, Indonesian, Philippines)</span></li>\n<li><span>Opportunity to challenge with big projects in businesses fields such as: Luxury Hotel</span></li>\n<li><span>Chains, shopping mall, Manufacturing etc.</span></li>\n<li><span>Others benefits such as holidays and insurance benefits follow Vietnamese law.</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "wiztech-vietnam", "job_name": "HCM Mid/Senior Fullstack .NET Developer (AngularJS/SQL)", "tag_list": "\n.NET\n\n\nSQL\n\n\nAngularJS\n", "location": "Floor 3, VVA Building, 279 Ly Tu Trong Street, Ben Thanh Ward, District 1, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Up to $4000\nCompulsory insurance full salary\nWorking in a dynamic and professional environment", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>Day-by-day Activities:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Develop custom software as part of an Agile Software Development Team.</li>\n<li>Participate in application development using Java, Spring Framework, JavaScript, Bootstrap, Hibernate and other technologies.</li>\n<li>Configure, analyze, design, develop, maintain and/or refactor new/existing program code and applications to support business processes and functions while minimizing technical debt as least as possible.</li>\n<li>Interface with all critical integration points to ensure that applications are integrating successfully and efficiently with the requested applications as necessary.</li>\n<li>Participate in problem solving and support troubleshoots for assigned applications, functional areas and projects.</li>\n<li>Develop and own knowledge of the assigned applications, functional areas and projects.</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Share technical and business domain knowledge with other team members.</li>\n<li>Be a subject matter expert across internal teams and assist in troubleshoots proactively.</li>\n<li>Work with internal team to ensure a smooth transition of assigned applications, functional areas and projects.</li>\n<li>Respond quickly and be responsible for developing and managing effective solutions to production issues.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Has a minimum of 2 years work experience in full stack development.</li>\n<li>Has actual hands-on experience and proficiency in AngularJS, ASP.NET Core, ASP.NET MVC, ASP.NET FORM</li>\n<li>Experience with relational databases and SQL – SLQ SERVER, MySQL, MongoDB.</li>\n<li>Experience working with GIT, Jenkins, Github, and CI/CD tools.</li>\n<li>Familiarity in cloud platforms such as Azure or AWS is a plus.</li>\n<li>Proficient in full software life cycle development.</li>\n<li>Knowledgeable with Agile methodology, particularly in Scrum framework.</li>\n<li>Good command in English communication skills is a plus.</li>\n<li>Receptive to learn new technologies.</li>\n<li>Vietnamese preferred.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><span><strong>1. Working environment</strong></span></p><ul>\n<li><span>Colleagues are friendly, sociable, support together</span></li>\n<li><span>Respectful working style.</span></li>\n</ul><p><span><strong>2. Competitive benefit packages</strong></span></p><ul>\n<li><span>13th salary &amp; Bonus</span></li>\n<li><span>Attractive salary with annual salary review</span></li>\n<li><span>Holiday: 14 annual leave days for Manager based on Vietnam Government regulations.</span></li>\n<li><span>Free refreshments including coffee, tea, and snack, parking fee..</span></li>\n<li><span>Team building, monthly party (birthday party)</span></li>\n<li><span>Open culture: employee is valued, treated fairly and trusted</span></li>\n<li><span>Have opportunity to work with overseas clients, global Projects</span></li>\n<li><span>Chance to work in a friendly, well-equipped environment with both foreigners</span></li>\n<li><span>(Singaporean, Japanese, Korean, Chinese, Malaysian, Indonesian, Philippines)</span></li>\n<li><span>Opportunity to challenge with big projects in businesses fields such as: Luxury Hotel</span></li>\n<li><span>Chains, shopping mall, Manufacturing etc.</span></li>\n<li><span>Others benefits such as holidays and insurance benefits follow Vietnamese law.</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "hdbank", "job_name": "Senior Innovation Specialist", "tag_list": "\nBusiness Analyst\n\n\nAgile\n", "location": "25 Nguyễn Thị Minh Khai, District 1, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Môi trường làm việc thân thiện, chuyên nghiệp\nLương thưởng tương xứng năng lực làm việc\nCó cơ hội phát triển bản thân", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>Trách nhiệm chính</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Tổ chức nghiên cứu và phân tích xu hướng thị trường hiện tại và tương lai về công nghệ và đề xuất cải tiến, mở rộng các dịch vụ của ngân hàng.</li>\n<li>Làm việc với các chủ quản của sản phẩm, kênh số để đề xuất các cải tiến sản phẩm, các quy trình hoạt động theo hướng số hóa.</li>\n<li>Thực hiện các nhiệm vụ khác theo phân công của cấp quản lý.</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Các công việc thực hiện chính</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Lập các báo cáo đề xuất, cải tiến, mở rộng việc số hóa và tự động hóa các dịch vụ của ngân hàng.</li>\n<li>Lên kế hoạch và làm việc với các chủ quản của sản phẩm, kênh số và đề xuất các cải tiến về sản phẩm, quy trình theo hướng sáng tạo và đổi mới trên nền tảng công nghệ số.</li>\n<li>Đề xuất các ý tưởng về sản phẩm/ dịch vụ số, quy trình vận hành số dựa trên kết quả nghiên cứu và khảo sát.</li>\n<li>Làm việc với các đối tác cung cấp giải pháp công nghệ trong và ngoài nước để tìm kiếm các ý tưởng mới nhằm cải tiến sản phẩm, dịch vụ số.</li>\n<li>Thực hiện các nhiệm vụ khác theo phân công của Cấp quản lý.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p><strong>Các yêu cầu về bằng cấp/chứng chỉ</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Tốt nghiệp Đại học chuyên ngành Công Nghệ Thông Tin hoặc những chuyên ngành có liên quan khác.</li>\n<li>Có kinh nghiệm trong lĩnh vực xây dựng hay cải tiến sản phẩm dịch vụ số trên nền tảng công nghệ số.</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Yêu cầu về kinh nghiệm/kiến thức</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Trên 3 năm kinh nghiệm về xây dựng sản phẩm dịch vụ số trong các ngân hàng hoặc công ty tài chính.</li>\n<li>Có kinh nghiệm về thiết kế dịch vụ số, phát triển ứng dụng cho các kênh số ứng dụng công nghệ. </li>\n<li>Có kinh nghiệm về phân tích xu hướng số hóa.</li>\n<li>Có kiến thức về chuyển đổi số trong lĩnh vực ngân hàng, tài chính.</li>\n<li>Có kinh nghiệm thực hiện các dự án số hóa và phương pháp làm việc Agile là một lợi thế</li>\n</ul><p><strong>Các yêu cầu khác về phẩm chất, tính cách/kỹ năng, khả năng</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Tiếng Anh giao tiếp</li>\n<li>Có khả năng phối hợp với nhiều đơn vị trong ngân hàng. </li>\n<li>Có tinh thần trách nhiệm cao, khả năng chịu áp lực công việc tốt.</li>\n<li>Khả năng làm việc độc lập và theo nhóm</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Thưởng 13,14 và KPI </li>\n<li>Bảo hiểm y tế, bảo hiểm tai nạn</li>\n<li>Du lịch nghỉ mát hằng năm</li>\n<li>Tăng lương định kì</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "rch-asia", "job_name": "Lead Mobile Developer (Android) ", "tag_list": "\nAndroid\n\n\nTeam Leader\n\n\nJava\n", "location": "PAX SKY, 13 Truong Dinh, Vo Thi Sau Ward, District 3, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Additional Private Insurance \nDaily Supply of Fruits, Drink \n13th Month Salary & Bonus", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>The candidates shall play a key role in this team by demonstrating:<br>• Manage the development and deployment processes – make sure that the features are shipped<br>optimally, and product stays healthy once they hit production.<br>• Design, review, write, and test code – this is a hands-on engineering role, and you will be<br>directly involved in the design and development of new features.<br>• Provide mentorship and feedback to teammates to make your team the best version of itself.<br>Motivate and encourage everyone to give their best work. </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>MUST HAVE<br><i><strong>Candidate is required to complete a test before being screened for the interview.</strong></i><br>• Consolidated knowledge of Android application development in Java (must have) and Kotlin<br>(advantage) language, in accordance with Clean Architecture guidelines, Object Oriented<br>Programming (OOP) and related Design Patterns, in particular MVVM<br>• Working knowledge of Software IDEs, in particular Android Studio<br>• Working knowledge of Internet Secure Communications (OWASP guidelines, including, REST<br>APIs, HTTPS, Certificates, etc.)<br>• Working experience with GIT and tracking systems like Jira<br>• Leading exp of a small team (2-5 members) of at least 2 years<br>• Knowledge of one or more of the following subjects will be considered:<br>o JetPack Compose; and/or,<br>o Dependency Injection; and/or,<br>o Testing: Unit Testing, Expresso 2.0; and/or,<br>o Continuous integration environments such as Jenkins, Bitbucket or others.<br>• “Can-do” attitude and passion to face challenges.<br>• Strong commitment to RCH goals and enthusiasm to learn new working methods and<br>technologies.<br>• Willing to work in a dynamic environment going beyond personal comfort zone.<br>• Clean, methodic and self-critical mindset in requirements acquisition, definition of use cases,<br>design and software implementation.<br>• Fluent written and spoken English, possibly German and/or French</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>CHẾ ĐỘ LƯƠNG THƯỞNG PHÚC LỢI<br>• 13th month salary (cycle: Jan – Dec. If the employee works for from 2 months to less than 6 months, he/she will be entitled to ½ 13th month salary; if the employee works for 6 months to 1 year, he/she will be entitled to a full 13th month salary);<br>• 100% salary in probation period;<br>• Subscription of the national social insurance scheme from probation (paid on gross salary);<br>• Subscription of PVI health care program after 2 months of probation;<br>• Yearly company trip;<br>• Periodic team-building activities;<br>• Yearly health examination;<br>• Transportation allowance: 20,000/working day in office;<br>• Lunch allowance: 700,000/month;<br>• Monthly attendance allowance: 400,000/month (after 2 months probation);<br>• Employee is to be given a laptop for work use.</p>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "hdbank", "job_name": "Product Design Leader", "tag_list": "\nUI-UX\n\n\nDesigner\n", "location": "25 Nguyễn Thị Minh Khai, District 1, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Môi trường làm việc thân thiện, chuyên nghiệp\nLương thưởng tương xứng năng lực làm việc\nCó cơ hội phát triển bản thân", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>As the Product Design Leader, you will oversee a team of product designers responsible for the end-to-end subscriber journey across all our products. We believe that designers do their best work when they are guided by empathetic and supportive managers, so you'll develop your team's skills and career aspirations and create a supportive culture for Product Design to flourish. You will improve the quality of our design work by advocating for our priorities with other teams and contributing to process and communication improvements.</p><p>You will be a member of HDbank, working alongside Program, Product, Engineering, Data, Research and Marketing counterparts to help translate strategy to operation by directly shaping our creative processes on the team. You will look across multiple cross-functional teams with a Product Design perspective to identify shared opportunities, transfer insights across platforms, and uncover nuances that require experiences to diverge. You will work with cross-functional partners and the product design team to prioritize work with the greatest impact for our users and our business.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Manage a team of product designers, including 1:1s, career development, and performance management.</li>\n<li>Organize design resources to improve effectiveness and efficiency.</li>\n<li>Guide the design work, ensure the design process runs smoothly, and deliver successful outcomes that improve the quality of the user experience.</li>\n<li>Provide direction on design work that challenges assumptions, encourages exploration, addresses user needs and ties to objectives, research and data.</li>\n<li>Identify projects that would benefit from a design-led strategy, and get alignment from partners and leadership.</li>\n<li>Own, handle and properly communicate escalations, providing clear information, advice and options to partners and upper management when help is needed.</li>\n<li>Create design concepts and drawings to determine the best product</li>\n<li>Present product ideas to relevant team members for brainstorming</li>\n<li>Suggest improvements to design and performance to product engineers</li>\n<li>Employ design concepts into functional prototypes</li>\n<li>Perform research on product technologies and structures to implement into design concepts</li>\n<li>Maintain up to date on current industry trends and market conditions</li>\n<li>Modify and revise existing designs to meet customer expectations</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Case studies of work that you guided a team through that illustrate your thought process and that demonstrate how you’ve coached your reports.</li>\n<li>Record of shipping excellent UX with impact, in a managerial capacity.</li>\n<li>Experience managing diverse teams and co-leading those teams with Product and Engineering partners.</li>\n<li>Comfort in using quantitative data and qualitative research to inform product and design decisions.</li>\n<li>Fluency with UX design principles and how they guide users' emotions and behaviors.</li>\n<li>Experience striking a productive balance between exploration and execution on a product design team, in an agile environment.</li>\n<li>Comfort with design and prototyping tools; express product design ideas in a visual and verbal manner, as the situation dictates, to align teams and partners.</li>\n<li>Ability to break down big challenges into smaller decisions framed as trade-offs (e.g. time vs. scope), and make decisions with urgency.</li>\n<li>Experience establishing and maintaining processes and defining goals/metrics to iteratively improve over time.</li>\n<li>Experience hiring and retaining diverse teams of designers and foster an inclusive culture where designers can do their best work.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul>\n<li>Full social insurance, health insurance, unemployment insurance according to Labor Laws</li>\n<li>Extract salary &amp; bonus, performance review 1time/year </li>\n<li>13th +14th salary bonus </li>\n<li>Very competitive salary</li>\n<li>12 days of annual leave</li>\n<li>Support for personal loan </li>\n<li>Friendly and supportive working environment</li>\n<li>Career growth opportunities.</li>\n<li><span>Team building activities</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}
{"company_name": "hdbank", "job_name": "Backend Developer (.Net/Java)", "tag_list": "\nJava\n\n\nMySQL\n\n\nOracle\n\n\nFresher Accepted\n", "location": "25 Nguyễn Thị Minh Khai, District 1, Ho Chi Minh", "three_reasons": "Môi trường làm việc thân thiện, chuyên nghiệp\nLương thưởng tương xứng năng lực làm việc\nCó cơ hội phát triển bản thân", "description": "<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<ul><li>Các dự án cần sự xây dựng backend hỗ trợ (kết nối đối tác) hoặc các dự án đã có sẵn nhân sự front-end; đòi hỏi nhân sự chuyên trách phát triển back-end</li></ul><p>- Phát triển các nội dung xử lý phía back-end theo yêu cầu dự án<br>- Phát triển API kết nối với front-end hay đối tác<br>- Đảm bảo các tiêu chuẩn bảo mật và mã hóa<br>- Tuân thủ quy trình/quy định của HDBank</p><p> </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>- Có ít nhất 3 năm kinh nghiệm trong lĩnh vực phát triển phần mềm ở vị trí backend<br>- Đã từng tham gia ít nhất 4-5 dự án trong đó đảm nhiệm việc phát triển back-end; hoặc 2 dự án lớn (có 5 người tham gia trở lên)</p><p>- Thành thạo với ngôn ngữ lập trình .Net/Java<br>- Có kinh nghiệm về PL/SQL <br>- Có kinh nghiệm phát triển  API Web Services, tương tác với API và sử dụng thành thạo các công cụ lập trình như Eclipse, Netbean<br>- Thành thạo về Java core Back-End, xử lý tốt Multithread (Xử lý tối thiểu 1000-2000 giao dịch cùng lúc), Multi-processing, cơ chế Hash table, cơ chế xử lý file.<br>- Có kinh nghiệm về các tiêu chuẩn bảo mật<br>- Thành thạo việc thiết kế CSDL trên DB Oracle, MS SQL …<br>- Có kinh nghiệm làm việc với các hệ điều hành Enterprise Linux, HP-UX<br>- Có kinh nghiệm về SVN, GIT, Jira;<br>- Có kinh nghiệm với các quy tắc thiết kế OOP;<br>- Có kinh nghiệm về các dự án ESB, Open API<br>- Có hiểu biết về Docker và Microservices<br>- Có hiểu biết vẽ MQ, cache...<br>- Có hiểu biết về mockup API</p><p>- Thành thạo việc xây dựng các tài liệu đặc tả kỹ thuật (Technical Specification Document), bao gồm: ERD, Database schema, swagger APIs,…<br>- Có khả năng đọc hiểu tài liệu tiếng Anh</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"job-details__paragraph\">\n<p>- Thưởng 13,14</p><p>- Thưởng theo xếp loại</p><p>- Bảo hiểm y tế, bảo hiểm tai nạn</p><p>- Du lịch nghỉ mát hằng năm</p><p>- Tăng lượng định kì</p>\n</div>"}
